name: De Zee

She is exhausted and drifts away from shore in the small rowing boat, out to sea. Everything seems lost. Fish swims in the high, wild waves to seek help. name: Будущее и прошлое тюрьмы, которую решено продать / Редакция контекст
summary:
The Kresty pre—trial detention center, which was put up for auction, is one of the largest and most famous insulators in Russia, which opened already in 1892 and during this time managed to acquire a legendary history. The Bolshevik Trotsky, the poet Brodsky, Marshal Rokossovsky, the actor Zhzhenov were sitting there, and Anna Akhmatova wrote the poem "Requiem" about the "Crosses" — one of the most poignant texts of the XX century.

In the new issue of "Editorial. Context" we decided to conduct a kind of tour of the "Crosses" — both the prison itself and the fate of its prisoners.

name: Parenthood's Sam Jaeger: Lucked Into It
summary: Sam Jaeger (Parenthood, The Handmaid's Tale) joins us this week and opens up on how the repetition of denial as an actor has him feeling like his last job will be his last, despite his success in hit shows like Devil in Ohio, Parenthood, and more. Sam talks about how he feels like he's made it haphazardly through life with his ADD and how later in adulthood he faced anxiety and depression. We also get into what it was like directing co stars on Parenthood, his iconic Gene Hackman stories, and how he feels like sloppy seconds for Owen Wilson and Ewan McGregor.

name: Don't Go Fund Me
summary: After an apartment fire made her homeless, a woman sues a former friend who offered her a place to stay, for a wrongful eviction and unwanted sexual advances while staying with him. He countersues for damages due to false accusations.

name: WTF Is An Accounting Operations Manager?!
summary: After finishing up the annual audit and having a fun summer, the Sunryzer accounting team is on Cloud 9. Hunter still hasn't made a move on Sarah, but that's okay... he's getting there... right? With the company preparing to go public, they bring onboard a new SEC Reporting Manager who... well, just doesn't seem to always have the best of luck. Things really start to get shifty when the CFO opens a new position. Sarah eyes a career progression into a new role at the company: Accounting Operations Manager, which throws the whole team into a tizzy. Not to mention, the sales team, led by Lance and former taco maker Rico under the leadership of the VP of Sales, are actively choosing to make it difficult for the accounting team to do their jobs.

name: That's Just Right - Episode 9: Discussing Up To C3E40 & The Mighty Nein Reunited
summary: Tis Critmas Season! Laura Bailey, Taliesin Jaffe, Matthew Mercer, and Liam O'Brien celebrate the holidays with cozy pajamas, Critmas carols, gift exchanges, and this episode of 4-Sided Dive!

name: The Boss Baby Christmas Bonus
summary: Christmas Eve takes a twisty turn when the Boss Baby accidently swaps places with one of Santa's elves and gets stranded at the North Pole.

name: Visitor From Another Dimension
summary: Hanzawa's mother comes to check out Beika — but then a hostage incident occurs, and she might be one of the victims!?

name: Darkness in the Light of the World
summary: In 2017, former members of LLDM form an online community on Reddit sharing stories of abuse at the hands of the church's venerated "Apostles". Groomed as children, and psychologically imprisoned within a cult-like society through indoctrination, familial pressures and strict, religious dogma, they were taught to surrender their free will (mind, body and soul) in return for eternal salvation. The survivor community expands and increases awareness while the church grows in prominence and spreads globally.

name: Unconditional
summary: Despite the church's expanding power and influence, award-winning investigative journalists Rhonda Schwartz and Brian Ross report on the decades-long scandal as law enforcement also takes note. Risking their own safety, ex-LLDM members come forward to speak out as the church plans the construction of a fundamentalist community in Georgia, USA.

name: A Fight for Justice
summary: In 2019, LLDM's incumbent "Apostle", Naasón Joaquín García is apprehended along with two of his alleged handmaidens and charged with crimes relating to five Jane Does. In a heartbreaking turn of events for Joaquín García's victims, prosecutors unexpectedly offer him a plea deal depriving the victims of their day in court. While Joaquín García is sentenced to just 16 years and eight months in jail, the survivors are determined to keep fighting for justice while grappling with their trauma.

name: Ashton & Michael Kutcher
summary: Ashton Kutcher shares his terrifying battle with a rare disease that almost took his life, and in their first interview together, he and his twin brother Michael share the emotional story of a childhood defined by extreme life and death health challenges. Michael talks about being born with cerebral palsy, then enduring a life-saving heart transplant at 13, and the brothers unravel a complicated relationship as twins with such different lives.

name: Oprah Winfrey & Maria Shriver
summary: Oprah Winfrey and her longtime friend, author and journalist Maria Shriver sit down with Dr. Agus to take an unflinching look at women's health, specifically a misunderstood and often mistreated issue: menopause.

name: Howie Mandel
summary: Comedian and television personality Howie Mandel talks to Dr. Agus about his debilitating, lifelong struggle with obsessive-compulsive disorder. Joined by daughter Jackelyn, who suffers from her own OCD and anxiety, we discover how Howie's obsession with control has impacted his life, his career and the people he loves most.

name: САМЫЕ ДИКИЕ ОШИБКИ ПО РАСПОЛОЖЕНИЮ ВЫКЛЮЧАТЕЛЕЙ #704
Didingwe
summary: A new detective joins the team, and Fanie has to embrace her past . The broken homes of the victims offer little clues, further building on the labyrinthine case.

name: NTS Renters - HIGE and ME, Tokyo
Wife #4 - When the World Ends
summary: Most is very crazy about his relationship with Achi that he almost cannot keep the secret. In the shooting set, Most treats Achi so well that Fern feels bad and worried. And during the shooting of an NC scene, Most and Achi shock everyone with their very real acting that their emotions are still bubbling after the cut. Most and Achi cannot control themselves anymore, they make love in the set's bathroom. Fern sees that, and feels shocked and sad, so she reveals that she is dating Achi. Unfortunately, someone recorded this moment and sent it to the reporters.

name: Sort of Opening
summary: On the eve of the opening of the new club-gallery, a moment between Bessy and Sabi creates tension in their relationship.

name: Sort of Janazah
summary: A family crisis causes Sabi to confront unresolved feelings towards their father.

name: Just Business
summary: As Steve's new calendar flies off the shelves, a fed-up Nick makes a pitch to New York investors. A snub from Steve provides Otis with a sobering wake-up call.

name: Who Committed Libel Against Reese Witherspoon?
Jim Wynorski
summary: This week on the Freakshow is a newly minted member of the Full Moon family and one of the most important B movie directors in history: the one, the only Jim Wynorski, director of THE LOST EMPIRE, CHOPPING MALL, BIG BAD MAMA 2 and THE RETURN OF THE SWAMP THING as well as the upcoming KILLBOTS!

name: Sea Monsters of the Depths
summary: In this week's episode, the monsters find themselves in dark water for this week's Sea Monster challenge while trying to avoid an early burial at sea.

name: The Child Inside of Her
summary: A shocking confession between the women changes everything. Steph opens up about the real reason she came to The Groove Hotel. Sparkle faces her fears with the help of an unconventional date.

name: What in the Malarkey
summary: Brooke pivots in an unanticipated direction. Sparkle juggles three big personalities on her group date. The cat is finally let out of the bag, leaving everyone at The Groove Hotel stunned.

name: The Mysterious Flight
summary: Jenni Rivera's death disrupts her triumphal comeback to Mexico.

name: The Mexican Connection
summary: The connection between Jenni Rivera and Mexican drug cartels becomes a potential source of concern.

name: Target or Victim
summary: Rocked by threats within her inner circle, Jenni decides to make significant changes in her life.

name: A Bedroom for Mom
summary: Tara and Percy renovate the bedrooms prepping for a visit from Tara's mom.

name: Episode 4
summary: With Claudia's revelation throwing the castle into chaos, breakfast reaches a dramatic climax, and the levels of distrust reach boiling point. Before the dust has even had a chance to settle, the players must momentarily put their differences aside as they face another mission, where they are given the chance to add a potential £10,000 to the already growing prize pot. And with a tense round table on the horizon, one player has an extremely difficult decision to make.

No Estúdio com o Ex Caribe S02E07

summary: In Molladalen, a climber slams into the rock face. The minutes get long as helicopters circle overhead without the ability to communicate.

name: Eksplosjonsfare
summary: An enormous gas tank in the center of Bergen is in danger of exploding. Does the brigade leader have to sacrifice Zachariasbryggen to save human life?

name: Juleleker
summary: Markus has made a new Christmas game that he is testing on the participants. They are in on the game, and one participant must endure the roasting. So go home!

name: Savnet i fossen
summary: Firefighters respond to a dramatic boat accident where three people are missing. It will be a demanding and long-lasting action.

name: Sovnet fra komfyren
summary: The fire brigade respond to what they believe to be a false alarm. In the middle of the dense wooden housing development in Bergen, a young man has fallen asleep with the stove on.

name: Tatt på sengen
summary: An automatic alarm wakes the firefighters, who think they are just going on a simple routine mission. Then comes the message that it really is on fire.

name: På min vakt
summary: Firefighters obviously don't hope that there will be a fire, but at the same time they love their job. Even when they have to clean up after a smelly fire.

name: World Tag League 2022 & Super Jr. Tag League 2022 Day 13
Dér Heni, Tóth Bence, Megyeri Csilla, Zdroba Patrik - Bakos Gergő, Tóth-Hódi Pamela, Molnár Zsolt, Bádoki Bettina

How to Find and Keep a Healthy Relationship

summary: Villa residents test the waters — and waste no time breaking rules — with new connections. Lana puts an unapologetic player on the spot to pick a date.

name: Officer Kill Joy
summary: One guy works to get out of the doghouse. With the group facing double penalties, a self-appointed "sex cop" tries to shut down frisky business.

summary: A night in the private suite puts one cuddly couple in the hot seat. Two new arrivals make waves when they pick partners for dates on the beach.

name: The Shower and the Glory
summary: A steamy and shockingly expensive shower inspires even more misbehavior. Heads turn, feelings get hurt and a workshop reveals some raw emotions.

name: The Fractured Job
summary: Eliot returns to his hometown and discovers that the run-off from an oil fracking company is now poisoning the water and the crew plots to take down the powerful man behind it all.

name: Death of Luftwaffe
summary: Outnumbered and outproduced, the once mighty Luftwaffe is battling to hold its own across three fronts. Every month brings new pain for the force. But the Luftwaffe still has a few tricks up its sleeves and can make the Allies bleed heavily. If only Hitler and the Nazi leadership weren't sabotaging its chances...

name: Chapter III: The Battle of the Slaughtered Lamb
summary: The young heroes led by Willow are pursued by assassins who have been infected by dark magic.

name: Episode 113
summary: Arm takes audiences behind the scenes of the GMMTV 2023 Showcase, Diversly Yours.

name: Three's a Crowd
summary: After a fight with his pregnant girlfriend, a man invites a female acquaintance to move in; they clash over a personal loan, car damages and assault.

name: Chapter Five: Across the Yule-Verse
summary: Scott learns the truth about how he came to be Santa.

name: Don't Cry Over Spilt Champagne
summary: Singles continue to be in control when they each couple up to complete a three-legged champagne tower building race in the Princess Piazza; at the most dramatic Sail Away ceremony of the season, someone jumps ship and someone is left abandoned.

name: Episode 1
summary: After an embarrassing incident at her brother Joey's wedding, Rosie Molloy decides to change her life by freeing herself of her many addictions. After a disastrous interaction in a pub with a yoga instructor, Rosie resolves to totally give up all her negative behaviours in order to gain Joey's trust, as well as support her dad through some difficult news. Comedy, starring Sheridan Smith.

name: Episode 2
summary: Rosie decides to reduce all substances and destructive behaviour by precisely half. But when a tragedy occurs, Rosie reverts to her old ways.

name: Episode 3
summary: Still reeling, Rosie agrees to attend a rehab facility but at the last minute changes her mind and escapes, legging it into the nearby countryside.

name: Episode 4
summary: Rosie accidentally takes meth and goes on an odyssey. She ends up at Ruby and Joey's house - where she discovers something shocking.

name: Episode 5
summary: Joey, Ruby, Nico and Win are not happy with Rosie. After going on the attack, Rosie tries to confide in her mother.

name: Episode 6
summary: Rosie panics that a failed drug test could get her fired and seeks to ger her hands on a counterfeit urine sample.

name: Tempest (Part 2)
summary: It just wouldn't be right wrapping up this season without him. The mane, the myth, and the legend John Glover, aka Lionel Luthor, joins Tom Welling and Michael Rosenbaum as we officially wrap up our rewatch of Season 1 of Smallville and the finale episode Tempest. It was a treat talking to Glover. He remembered what it was like going from a guest star to a regular, how deep the theme of family was in the show, and his true opinion on the character of Lionel Luthor. The guys close the episode by discussing some of the fan voted ‘best of' moments from Season 1. Any nominations and/ or selections surprise you?

name: Episode 9
summary: Sooheon revisits Sa Jungkyung's camping car, but it is a trap.

name: Episode 10
summary: Osung feels betrayed as his plan fails. Chanmi makes a shocking discovery as she sets up a trap.

name: Connection
summary: Dong-soo loses an eye to an organ hunter, and is then connected to the vision of a corpse artist.

name: Conjunction
summary: Dong-soo chases the corpse art killer with whom his vision is connected.

name: Composition
summary: Dong-soo becomes a murder suspect, while the killer is now aware of Dong-soo.

name: Confession
summary: Dong-soo tells his secret to Detective Choi, and I-rang tells Dong-soo the truth. Jin-seop sets a trap.

name: Concoction
summary: Odds are stacked against Dong-soo as he tries to rescue Z and the junkyard owner from Jin-seop.

name: Confusion
summary: I-rang and Detective Choi set out to Jin-seop's atelier but their conflicting interests stir up chaos.

name: Yesterday Is Gone, Tomorrow Is Unknown "The Present"
summary: A conversation that brings closure only causes more misunderstandings.

name: Episode 8
summary: Shokun followed Maito to Chang Rai and Maito was surprised that Shokun came. Meanwhile, Gap went to Namwa's house to try to make up with her with the help from Kanoon. This is when both of them got to patch things up. Shokun tried to make up with Maito by appeasing him so much that an accident occured in the tea plantation. Green who was trying to score some point with Maito got fed up and later on found the perfect moment to confess to Maito but suddenly everyone have to come back to Bangkok right away. The reason was Ford called and told them Evening Sunday got into the final round in the competition. CopterMaipai fandom got even more chaotic when Star exposed that Fruitylove was Sasaengs!

name: Ester Expósito, la Constitución y lágrimas de París
La grande bugia di Natale
summary: In a moment of weakness during a stressful dinner conversation about her status as a single person, Gianna makes up a story to please her nosy family.

name: Biciclette
summary: With only 20 days to go, Gianna intensifies her search. But venturing back into dating proves more difficult than learning how to ride a bike again.

name: Tu sei speciale
summary: Feeling vulnerable after her club encounter and a tough shift at the hospital, Gianna agrees to go out with a prominent patient.

name: Punti di vista
summary: Gianna becomes the center of attention at a chaotic Christmas party for the hospital staff that ends in an unexpected boat ride home.

name: La festa è finita
summary: When even Titti appears to have found love, Gianna makes an ill-advised decision that releases a rollercoaster of emotions.

name: Come in un presepe
summary: With Christmas rapidly approaching, tragedy seems to be piling on — until an unusual day at work shifts Gianna's perspective.

name: Episode 8
summary: The summer training camp is over, and the fall tournament is near. The four members of the Kyoritsu sumo club are determined to win their first match. However, Ryota is unable to stay focused as he is uncertain about how he feels about that night with Saki. Meanwhile, Kawarada from the ekiden club joins the sumo club, creating a team of five. In the women's tournament, Honoka is matched up against Mayu.

name: Cuando Álex encontró a Bruno
summary: A misplaced voicemail connects hunky bartender Álex with Bruno, a movie-loving architect. Álex's friend Vero mulls over big next steps in her life.

name: Las alas de Ícaro
summary: Álex and Bruno's first date turns out to be a rollercoaster ride. Bruno's friends Albert and Núria meet with a potential new nanny before a night out.

name: La fiera de mi niña
summary: Bruno and Álex both wake up feeling confused about how to navigate the morning after. Albert struggles at work. Patri and Vero try to reconnect.

name: Volver a empezar
summary: While Álex agonizes over texting Bruno back, Vero and Patri venture into the world of dating apps. Bruno's co-worker Ramón surprises him.

name: Cada oveja en su corral
summary: At three different celebrations, unexpected guests and revelations make for a memorable Christmas Day.

name: Un grado de separación
summary: Álex and Bruno cross paths again. Javi offers Ramiro a sympathetic ear. Vero and Albert both experience moments of clarity.

name: Cinco minutos antes de la cuenta atrás
summary: A rowdy New Year's Eve party at Bar Bero brings everyone together for a night full of songs, cava and — for better or worse — honest conversations.

name: El hilo rojo
summary: Patri and Vero prepare to move into their new apartment and Ramiro resolves to move on. Álex and Bruno can't seem to break the red thread of destiny.

name: La fuente
summary: As a new school year starts, Mich is tired of being invisible to the popular kids — including her own boyfriend — and sets out to make a splash.

name: Nací lista
summary: Mich discovers that Mati is a DJ, creating the perfect opportunity to go to a real party for the first time. But her grand plan hits a few snags.

name: La nueva
summary: Dani continues his quest to get Mich back, but she only has eyes for Mati — who's dating Brenda. A group project puts Yadi in an awkward situation.

name: Una protagonista como yo
summary: Brenda shows Mati another side of her life. Mich is so excited to try out for the school play that she can barely focus on anything else.

name: Amiga, date cuenta
summary: Audition results for "Alice in Xochiland" cause drama at school and at home. Mich and Dani both get to know Majo better.

name: Código P
summary: After the students get sent home from school early because of a lice outbreak, they spend an educational afternoon on the canals.

name: Hipocondría
summary: Just when Mich could really use some good advice, Tania and Yadi read her the friendship riot act. Is it any wonder she feels like she's dying?

name: Al fin del mundo
summary: Mich convinces Mati to hit the road for an impromptu visit to see her dad. Majo feels like a fish out of water at Dani's family party.

name: La primera vez
summary: Dani plans a big night with Mich, who's been busy making amends. Brenda maneuvers to take out her onstage competition.

name: Octágono amoroso
summary: Will Mich be Alice or La Flor? Is she in love with Dani, Mati or Majo? With her head and heart spinning, Mich takes center stage.

name: I feel like a piece of meat
All Exclusive med Iben Hjejle
summary: Casper Christensen and Iben Hjejle broke up ten years ago, and the former couple have not really talked about the breakup since. Now they have to spend a whole day together.

name: Boğaz Havası İyi Gelir
summary: Agah is found dead and all the murders point towards Fuat. The organization lends a helping hand.

name: Who Can Get To The Most States In 4 Days
The Grooveyard
summary: The leading ladies make peace with their past to make room for their future. Steph and Sparkle double date. The women's villa gets steamy as Brooke invites one man over to her place.

name: We Didn't Come Here for the Bros
summary: The underdog goes deep on his long-awaited date with Sparkle. Steph makes an unexpected connection. Brooke does something on a very intimate date that she can never take back.

name: Midcentury Modern Update
summary: Sarah designs a living room space that embraces its midcentury aesthetic.

name: Winter Wonderland
summary: The One Zoo Three brothers create a winter wonderland at the zoo, with special festive treats for the Amur tigers. Meanwhile, Tim and Tam the Tapirs tuck into a winter vegetable challenge!

name: Episode 5
summary: Tempers around the round table are more frayed than ever as another player is sent home. With the traitors set to murder again, the faithful are even more determined to catch a traitor in the act. But not even the traitors are prepared for the surprises in store during the mission, as Claudia proves that the castle really is full of secrets.

name: Chapter 1: Boom-Ooh-Yatatatah
summary: In the wake of Kim Philby's escape to Moscow, his closest friend in Britain's Secret Service, Nicholas Elliott, is under investigation.

name: Chapter 2: The Admiral's Glass
summary: Investigator Lily Thomas understands that Elliott is never going to divulge anything of value in a conventional interrogation process so she manipulates him.

name: Chapter 3: Allegory of the Catholic Faith
summary: Philby begins to understand that the KGB can never fully trust him now that he's in Moscow and as far as they're concerned his life as a spy for them is over.

name: Chapter 4: Vodka
summary: Elliott rattles Blunt's cage to make him panic and then follows him to a clandestine meeting in the middle of the night.

name: Chapter 5: Snow
summary: Elliott and Lily fear that no one can be trusted. They must get to Blunt before anyone else to interrogate him and confirm their suspicions.

name: Chapter 6: No Man's Land
summary: Lily has forced Elliot to remember more than he perhaps ever wanted to about Philby. Months later, Elliott receives a letter from Philby asking for a meeting in an East Berlin bar.

name: Episode 1
summary: London, 1826: When prominent society couple Mr. and Mrs Benham are found stabbed to death, their maid Frannie Langton is accused of murder.

name: Episode 2
summary: Frannie and Madame's illicit relationship develops. Meanwhile, we learn about the horrific experiments conducted at the Paradise plantation.

name: Episode 3
summary: Frannie and Madame's relationship comes under threat as jealousies flare in the Benham house, and Madame's own issues worsen.

name: Episode 4
summary: Frannie stands trial. The shocking truths about the Benhams' murders, Langton's experiments and Frannie's past are revealed.

name: Episode 1
summary: Jonny has been battling with his mental health, so when he is hit by a family tragedy, his struggles intensify.

name: Episode 2
summary: Mei gets closer to Jonny, but is hiding behind a big lie, while Louis has a house party and falls for Zia. The gang go clubbing and Mei's behaviour get Neve into hot water.

name: Episode 3
summary: Louis wants to lose his virginity and Jonny gives him advice, but when the moment comes, it isn't exactly how he planned. Neve realises she has feelings for Jonny.

name: Episode 4
summary: Neve's sister Timmi comes to stay while their parents are away. Jonny is avoiding Mei and Neve is relieved that he is moving on, but events take a dramatic turn.

name: Episode 5
summary: Regan struggles with the loss of control when her nan's care is taken over, and the gang goes to a careers fair, where Neve sees Marcus in a new light.

name: Episode 6
summary: After the attack, Mei wants to move back to Canada. Jonny makes a shocking discovery and Marcus decides he's not keen on Neve's partying side.

name: #166 - H-E-B Center in Cedar Park, TX
I møte med frykten
summary: Help finally arrives in Molladalen. The rescuer must assess the condition of the injured person before the lifting can be started.

name: "Nostalgic New Year's Eve Soup with rice cake"
Episode 3
summary: Seon Heo and Mu Yeong drink together after work. Drinking through the night, Seon Heo suddenly asks to draw Mu Yeong naked?

name: Juleverksted
summary: No time before Christmas without a Christmas workshop! It turns out to be both cozy and stressful.

name: В гостях: Alisha и Тим Сорокин
Kleine Doekoe
summary: When Detective Martin arrives at a crime scene where a shooting has taken place, he gets the shock of his life. One of the victims of the shooting is an acquaintance of his. A criminal of the old order, but also a father figure to Martin. Shortly after the murder, someone contacts him. There must be room for a new criminal generation with different rules: if you don't cooperate, you get a bullet.

name: Tarik Mesina
summary: The police find a murdered detective. A special team from outside is assigned to the case. When Rob and Rachid patrol together for the first time, they drive straight into every police officer's nightmare. Tarik discovers that the murdered detective was corrupt. That puts everything and everyone on edge. Willem tries to convince Martin to join Dwight's organization.

name: Kroongetuige
summary: Martin lies to those closest to him out of self-defense. But not every lie goes unnoticed. Under pressure from Dwight, Willem continues to push Martin: what is the name of the key witness? When Martin discovers that name, he finds out that passing on the name will cost him dearly. He loses control and anxiously tries to regain control.

name: De Bankier
summary: Noura finds herself losing Martin more and more and tensions between them continue to rise. Henk's funeral takes place, but this is brutally disrupted by Dwight's men. Rachid is interrogated by Judith, who puts a lot of pressure on him. Tarik pushes the interrogation of a key witness to Martin. During the interrogation, the witness comes up with information that could endanger Martin's life.

name: Rob Lost Het Op
summary: Tarik and Martin visit the address that Frits gave to Martin. The resident appears to be a familiar face. Noura and Gülsah take on Judith, each with their own ammunition and motives. The list of corrupt cops adds fuel to the fire and Martin has to do everything he can to be the first to get his hands on the list. When Martin doesn't show up for an appointment with Dwight, Dwight decides to leave a clear message.

name: Inferno
summary: Martin and Noura spend the day in the hospital waiting for Max to wake up. A wave of violence ensues and Martin is left powerless. In the end he sees a way out to erase all traces that lead to him. Willem and Martin go looking for Dwight to settle the score. Tarik makes a discovery that could destroy Martin's double life forever.

name: Konserten
summary: With eight new songs, the entire stay will end with an insane party at a sold-out Meiriet in Sogndal. There will be sing-alongs, skaoling and a surprise lecture from the artist behind Firkantfar.

name: Mention très bien
summary: It is an important day for Hanane: the results of her exams. Her best friends Ambre and Maïssa are by her side, but she misses her brother. She has had no news from him for six months. Hanane is willing to tell a big lie to make him come back.

name: Câlin
summary: Determined to find out who had it in for her brother, Hanane persuades her friends to help her. The girls turn into razor-sharp investigators.

name: Les guetteurs
summary: Hanane charges headfirst into the drug dealers' universe. Julien, Djamel's childhood friend, tries to warn her of the dangers. Maïssa battles to save her brothers while Ambre takes a big decision.

name: Déter
summary: Hanane takes huge risks to meet the mysterious Chopin. Julien protects her as best he can. While Ambre is captivated by a charismatic dancer, Maïssa attempts the impossible to prevent her brothers from going into care.

name: Les barbus
summary: While the three friends are troubled by their affairs of the heart, Hanane discovers a new lead about who assaulted Djamel.

name: Toxique
summary: Hanane is confused as to which lead to follow. Ambre sinks into a toxic relationship. Maïssa makes a discovery about Hanane's new friend Bilal.

name: Animal nocturne
summary: Settling of scores, revelations and new threats follow on from each other. Faced with these obstacles, the three friends pull together, even if that means taking revenge.

name: Frère
summary: Chopin puts increasing pressure on Hanane and her entourage. Ambre takes a radical decision, while Maïssa is incapable of making a choice in her love life.

name: Le mytho
summary: Djamel has awoken from his coma. The truth comes out and is not always easy to hear.

name: Séparées on sera jamais seules
summary: Chopin carries out his threats. Hanane, Ambre and Maïssa debate on the best tactic to adopt to save Djamel and Julien.

name: Pay-Per-View
summary: The BAU hunts for the next connection to the serial killer network when they pursue a home invasion team. Alvez and Garcia convince Tyler Green to submit a cognitive interview to unlock his memories of Sicarius.

name: Call of the Wild
summary: Bells Hells travel deep into the Gloomed Jungles with the Gorgynei to seek a godly trial that may help Chetney's plight…

name: Doom Patrol
summary: As they struggle to function as a cohesive group, the Doom Patrol are confronted by a horrifying realization in the future.

name: Butt Patrol
summary: A desperate Doom Patrol strategize ways to wipe out the zombie butts… and reverse their grim future.

name: Kate Hudson Stays Positive While Eating Spicy Wings
summary: Kate Hudson is an Academy Award–nominated actress and entrepreneur with a portfolio that includes everything from King St. Vodka, to INBLOOM beauty and wellness products. You can catch her in the long-awaited film, Glass Onion: A Knives Out Mystery, which will be available globally on Netflix December 23rd. But how is she with spicy food? Find out as the Hollywood icon takes on the wings of death and discusses singing with Bruce Springsteen, making rom-coms with Matthew McConaughey, and the enduring appeal of Almost Famous.

name: Highway Men and Whores
summary: The team travels to the historic market town of Bridgnorth where they uncover a crime of the century at an old inn. Barri gets more than he bargained for.

name: 51 and Done.
summary: Democrats will have 51 Senate seats after Raphael Warnock wins the final election of the 2022 midterms, Donald Trump racks up more losses and legal troubles, and Strict Scrutiny's Kate Shaw joins to break down two major cases heard by the Supreme Court this week on gay rights and democracy.

name: Ставка ТВ - Эгриси. Два шага до финала
STICHTING AED BEHEER NEDERLAND: OVER DE LEVENSGEVAARLIJKE AED'S VAN GEERT KOLLEN
Heartless
summary: Q enlists Simon and K's help; Sgt. Turner and Goodnight's car is stolen.

name: College

name: Как советский подполковник предотвратил ядерную войну / Редакция
summary:
Soviet Lieutenant Colonel Stanislav Petrov, who prevented a nuclear war in 1983, became a media figure in the West in the 90s. There they made films about him, wrote a book, Kevin Costner, Robert De Niro and Matt Damon met with him.

Very few people in Russia still know about Petrov. As well as about the circumstances of that night from September 25 to 26, 1983.

Now that nuclear war has become a real possibility again, we decided that we simply have to share this story with you — the story of Stanislav Petrov, a Soviet officer who was not afraid to take responsibility not to start World War III.

name: Great Reputations
summary: Though finally the new queen of Constance, Monet yearns for a real rivalry with Julien. Meanwhile, Obie asks for Julien's help managing their friends ahead of meeting Grace's family.

name: Ghost in the Machine
summary: When the crew gets trapped in the holodeck by a mysterious malfunction, they aren't sure what's programmed or what's real.

name: The Essex College Food Workers Strike
summary: Leighton grapples with "dating up" for the first time. Kimberly appeals to an unlikely source for help with the food workers' strike. Whitney sets out to crush her final lab. Bela's faces blowback from a misstep.

name: Pre-Frosh Weekend
summary: For Pre-Frosh Weekend, Bela hosts her nerdy childhood friend Priya, who's had a surprise glow-up. Leighton prepares to come out to her dad. Kimberly seeks commonalities with Jackson, while Whitney finds chemistry with her lab partner.

name: Celebrity Look-alike
summary: Painted with Raven's iconic Snatch Game is back! The artists each impersonate the look of their favorite celebrity. Mariah Carey's makeup artist Kristofer Buckle guest judges.

name: Il magistrato buono
summary: Investigating magistrate Nino Scotellaro is on the trail of Mariano Suro. He has been hunting the fugitive boss of Cosa Nostra for years. This time he really is just one step away from catching him. But when the arrest fails, a furious Nino points his finger at the institutions, which he believes are accomplices. This accusation, however, will backfire, eventually taking everything away from him.

name: Talpe
summary: Everyone is convinced that Nino Scotellaro is dead, including his wife Luvi and his sister Leonarda. In reality, Nino is alive in a remote village. He is a guest of Don Salvatore Tracina, the only person who can help him. An unlikely alliance begins between the two that will transform the magistrate Nino Scotellaro into the Mafioso Balduccio Remora.

name: Tu quoque...
summary: Now that Nino is "free" again, it is hard for him not to think about his previous life. But the desire to avenge all he has lost takes over. And so, in his new identity as a Mafioso, he becomes part of another "family": the Tracinas, a clan in decline, rivals to Suro. Together with them, he begins his revenge. To fight Suro, though, they need weapons.

name: Gran finale
summary: The Grand Finale is here! The finalists will become the first Italian drag band performing their first unreleased track in a singing and dancing challenge. The time has finally come for the coronation. On the runway, the queens must show their most iconic Eleganza Extravaganza. Who will be Italy's Next Drag Superstar?

name: Round 1: Drag Raid
summary: The den is finally open! The "Drag Lord" Manila Luzon, together with her "drag dealer" Nicole Cordovez, and "drag runner" Sassa Gurl welcome the eight aspiring queens as they embark on an eight-week dragventurous competition showcasing their wit, talent and beauty to become the first Pinoy drag supreme.

name: Rag Doll Dog and Hairy Situation
summary: In this episode, the Judge rules on two cases. Up first, two Pit Bulls jump over a fence and maul a neighbor's small dog; the Judge speaks to the responsibility that comes with owning dangerous dog breeds. In the next case, a woman sues a hairstylist claiming money owed for improperly installing a wig and destroying it.

name: Las Vegas Raiders at Los Angeles Rams
summary: SoFi Stadium, Inglewood, CA.

name: 5 الحلقة
summary: A regretful Ahmad asks for Rawan's forgiveness. Rawan looks into Salma's belongings in hopes of solving the mystery. Ahmad's father-in-law tries to sideline him.

name: 8 December 1943
summary: Japanese planes bomb Calcutta when it is still being crushed by the weight of the Bengali famine. Adolf Hitler and Albert Speer are obsessively trying to increase war production so Germany can begin launching its vengeance weapon against Britain. The wars of resistance continue across the Balkans with continued brutality and a new resistance force emerges in Italy.

name: 1st generation SHINHWA WDJ, challenges the 4th generation idol dance!
San Francisco
summary: This week on Emeril Tailgates, we meet 49ers superfan Raul Villa in San Francisco. Join us as we create some crowd-pleasing seafood dishes inspired by the famous fresh fish of the Bay Area.

name: Episode 8
summary: The Juad Juad guys visit popular TikTok creators, Tee and Bie for some tips on becoming TikTok stars.

name: Especial de Natal - Episódio 1
summary: In December 2021, on Christmas Eve, Leo makes a naive request, but one that deeply affects Valentina.

name: Episode 2
summary: Becoming a CEO overnight, In Seong corrects injustice with the absolute power he gained on the first day at work. As he tracks Seon Ju's whereabouts on the day of the accident, suspicion against Ms. Jung, who may be a reliable ally or a deadly enemy, starts to grow.

name: Change
summary: After enduring years of abuse from his peers, Park Hyeong-seok moves to a different neighborhood to start a new life. Big changes are coming for him.

name: New Life
summary: Hyeong-seok attends school in his new body by day and works a part-time job as his true self by night – only to learn that nothing has really changed.

name: Friends
summary: A student by the nickname Basco helps the old Hyeong-seok fight off bullies, while the new Hyeong-seok hangs out with his first-ever group of friends.

name: Mom
summary: Hyeong-seok takes his mother out to a cafe as his transformed self. Basco seethes with righteous indignation when he spots the two together.

name: Kindness
summary: Hyeong-seok lends a hand to other struggling peers in school, while an enigmatic classmate offers him help and gifts when he needs it most.

name: Recommendation
summary: Pyeon Deok-hwa considers performing at the school festival, while others in his class relentlessly try to trample on his dream of becoming a rap artist.

name: Special Training
summary: Under Deok-hwa's direction, Hyeong-seok unlocks his singing potential as their musical collaboration nurtures their blossoming friendship.

name: Wall
summary: Competition heats up backstage on the day of the festival. Hyeong-seok and Deok-hwa leave their past and fears behind to deliver a song from the heart.

name: The End of the Long Wait
summary: Jung Woo decides to publish a book under his own name, so Tae Young invites Jung Woo to move into his home and use it as an office.

name: Us Back Then
summary: Tae Young begins to help Jung Woo in writing as an assistant, but Jung Hyun still doesn't give up on making things right with Jung Woo.

name: Episode 1
summary: As Harry shares the impact of a childhood in the public eye, he and Meghan reflect on the secret, early days of their unexpected romance.

name: Episode 2
summary: In 2016, the relationship becomes public — and public scrutiny begins. Meghan remembers school, family life, acting and activism before Harry.

name: Episode 3
summary: The couple's 2017 engagement sparks both cynicism and hope. As Meghan grapples with royal protocols, tabloid headlines begin to involve her family.

name: À l'origine
summary: By fate or coincidence, Marlène Cormier, Paul-André Denis and François Bibeau are reunited again. In this story of reunion where yesterday, today and tomorrow intertwine, we delve into the the universe and secrets of each character. What will François' return bring about in the lives of all these people?

name: 120 battements par minute
summary: Marlene is reluctant to reconnect with François, while Paul-André feels the need to get closer to his old friend. Moreover, Marlene seems troubled by every mention of Sylvie's name. Tomas' release from hospital worries his family. What is the source of his uneasiness? Céleste, Tomas' neighbor, tries to get closer to him. The recent death of his mother completely paralyzes Édouard. Why is he hiding the truth about his last outing with her?

name: Cambridge
summary: François Bibeau is invited with his two children to Paul-André and Renaud's house. The idea displeases Edward. Céleste is afraid to meet her neighbor Tomas. The meeting takes place, the past resurfaces. Marlene's stay in Cambridge has left deep and lasting traces. Marlène and Édouard are caught up in their secret. The death of his wife and Marlène's presence stirs François more and more. Marlène confided in Sylvie during dinner. The mystery around Tomas begins to unravel.

name: Les mères
summary: François goes to Paul-André, Renaud and Marlène's cottage, much to Marlène's dismay. Renaud understands François' grief and confusion over the death of his wife, and understands his desire to get closer to his old friends. Renaud confides in Jacynthe's mother, Simone, about the confrontation he had the day before with her son, Tomas. Céleste finds Tomas in a terrible state. Haunted by his mother's departure, Édouard breaks down. At the cottage, Marlène is disturbed by François' revelations, giving a new perspective to her meeting with Sylvie. An incident disrupts the tennis match between Renaud and François.

name: Les morts-vivants
summary: The life of Renaud, Marlène and Paul-André takes a new turn. François supports his friends as they go through a rough patch. Tomas pushes Édouard to the limit. Marlène reveals a big secret to Céleste, which brings her closer to Tomas.

name: Not So New Beginnings

name: Rock the Boat
summary: Alexia finally celebrates her nuptials on a luxe yacht, but Lisa and Larsa rock the boat.

name: Date Night Disaster
summary: Alexia questions whether Adriana's wedding date is married; Lisa's date night with Lenny goes awry.

name: Hot Mic in Miami
summary: Julia worries Martina may leave her; Lisa hosts a pool party where Lenny shares his true intentions.

name: What Does It Take
summary: Hazel tries her hand at directing and pairs Regina with a rapper for a music video, and Gary basks in his newfound success and fame but longs for Bree's support.

name: Standing in the Shadows of Love
summary: Bree attempts to spend quality time with Gary after weeks of traveling and long-distance parenting, Hazel struggles to tell Regina an uncomfortable truth, and Jayla's game night hits a snag.

name: Troubling Revelations
summary: Dikahn searches for Andrew, Ruth challenges Marva's authority when a secret about The Highest is exposed, and unexpected visitors at the gates put the camp on high alert.

name: The Great Escape
summary: Joan gets some surprising news about two aspiring Raku members, Lewis recruits River to help secure the compound, and Brian and Lynn's escape hits a snag.

name: Dilapidated
summary: Andrew is in a standoff with Dikahn's men and Sheriff Conley, Marva enlists Zane to bring Lacey back into the fold, and Ruth has The Highest right where she wants him.

name: Upside Down
summary: Hilda confronts Alice about her betrayal, Darla sends Greg mixed signals after their failed date, John deals with an unwanted houseguest, and Regina accuses Bill of cheating.

name: How Are Quasiparticles Different From Particles?
Vantablack

Killer Curves

name: John Saponaro and Matt Isbill
summary: On this season finale of "Inside Monster Jam," John Saponaro and Matt Isbill join Scott Jordan to discuss life on the road and preview the 2023 Arena and Stadium Championship Series.

name: I Am Ruth
summary: Ruth, a loving and concerned mother, witnesses her teenage daughter Freya retreating into herself as she becomes more and more consumed by the pressures of social media.

name: Episode 6
summary: With the stakes getting higher and the faithful feeling like they are on the back foot, can they change the course of the reality game and put the traitors under fire? With life-changing money still at stake, the players must also remain focused on building the prize pot in a mission that sees them sink to new depths of despair. But that's the least of their worries, with an explosive round table on the horizon.

Episode 3

Sandra Oh & Duran Duran

summary: In space, no one can hear you scream — but can they hear you sing "Spice Up Your Life"? The cast of the Apple Original is determined to find out.

summary: The iconic Chicago band goes on an adventure with megafan Nikki, featuring a cameo by the great Mavis Staples and a Ferris Bueller homage.

summary: Hillary and Chelsea turn to their gutsy pal Amber for support as they sing along to empowering anthems — with an assist from Vanessa Williams.

name: The Bacon Brothers
summary: This duo celebrates their longtime band by covering songs from other sibling acts — plus, Michael teases Kevin for his years of fashion fails.

name: Method Man & Chris Redd
summary: From Stevie Wonder to DMX — and even Nickelback — the rapper/actor and comic riff through their playlist and a round of Black Facts.

name: Ciara & Russell Wilson
summary: The power couple combine their passions as they sing along to Ciara's bangers and hit the football field for a climactic pass.

summary: Zhou initiates war. Khader tries to stop Kavita's article from printing. Maurizio seeks revenge. Lin says his goodbyes.

summary: A young Korean boy befriends a legendary DJ who gives a much-needed boost to a hat shop owned by the boy's family.

name: The 9th Caller
summary: A Sri Lankan immigrant enters a Texas-sized contest to win a new car. As exhaustion sets in, she recalls her fraught relationship with her father.

summary: Determined to win the Minnesota State Fair, a chef must contend with shipping delays, a ticking clock, and his Somali community's judgement.

name: Space Door
summary: A Belarusian woman in New York is finally reunited with the man of her dreams after years kept apart. Will their love story pick up where it left off?

name: Columbus Starlings LLC
summary: A Japanese mother devotes her life to creating an all-woman baseball league in Ohio.

name: Paper Piano
summary: An Afghan piano prodigy seeking asylum in NYC fights to bring his mother to the US and reconnect with his passion.

name: The Indoor Arm
summary: Season finale. A woman from El Salvador who is an amputee adjusts to living in Beverly Hills and struggles to connect with sister's new life.

name: The 12 Hours of Christmas
summary: In the first holiday season since Ian and Poppy's departure, David grabs the reins and tries to infuse the team with Christmas spirit.

name: Which Is The Worst Food Crime? (Game)
Goat Head Taco
summary: New revelations about Casa Roja leave Allie trapped working with a local drug lord, forcing Margot to take the family's future into her hands.

name: Norah Jones is no longer fragile!
Drinking Games
summary: River gets cozy in the Cotswolds while searching for a sleeper agent. Min discovers Russian drinking games are the most brutal of all.

We Reject Your Influence
summary: Amber reaches her final destination at a Venezuelan black site. She's told she will die there.

summary: Shea and Syd create a drool-worthy kitchen remodel for one of their own team members — complete with a custom range hood and butler's pantry.

summary: A mom and son hope to bring modernity to their home while keeping some granny-chic elements. But Shea finds a chicken motif that needs to fly the coop.

summary: A family wants their toy room to be sophisticated enough to double as a guest room. Shea finds a way to install playful touches, like a climbing wall.

name: Family Trailer Rebuild
summary: Syd has a surprise for Shea: he bought an Airstream! Out of her comfort zone, Shea imagines one tricked-out trailer — but is her vision even possible?

name: Primary Bath Reconnected
summary: Sick of their "his-and-hers" bathrooms, a Salt Lake City couple asks Shea to knock down the wall between them... as well as add a splashy new feature.
