summary: Amelia meets UFC fighters Paddy and Molly for a date in Nabzy's in their hometown of Liverpool.

name: Islington Kebab (Essex Road)
summary: Yo peoples, took my talents over to Angel to see if this spot I frequently fly by was worth stopping off at. It was not.

name: Where there's Smoke
summary: With Beauty and Sbu expecting their first child, tensions run high as the Sello and Twala families are forced to reunite for the shower.

name: A Moth to the Flame
summary: After the baby shower ends in flames, the Sellos wind up at the Twala lodge for Christmas. Secrets swirl as everyone tries to hide their wrongdoings.

name: Like a House on Fire
summary: As various truths finally come to light, the Sellos and Twalas must put the past behind them and come together to help Beauty in her time of need.

name: The Power of Love
summary: Maximo doubles down on his new life with Isabel. Sara receives a potentially life-changing offer.

name: The Cruelest Month - Part One
summary: Gamache returns to Three Pines to investigate the disappearance of the popular resident Marc Fortier but it soon becomes a murder case that leads Gamache and his team into the heart of the village's dark past at St Anthony's. Meanwhile, Lacoste discovers a key piece of evidence relating to Blue's disappearance has been faked, and with Gamache's encouragement secretly reopens the case.

name: The Cruelest Month - Part Two
summary: The villagers confront the truth of their past and exorcise their collective demons as Gamache makes a breakthrough in the murder case and realises Marc's killer had a very personal motive. Meanwhile, Lacoste makes a discovery relating to Blue's disappearance that seems to identify a key suspect.

name: Molly
summary: Lizzie's Caring Paws Club comes up with an idea that's just what Charles needs to help a misunderstood rottweiler puppy.

name: Teeny & Tiny
summary: Charles and Lizzie disagree on whether or not to separate two puppy siblings. Thankfully, they find the perfect compromise.

name: Lucky
summary: After Lizzie and Charles are each let down by friends, a stray mixed-breed pup teaches them valuable lessons about trust and friendship.

name: Buddy
summary: The kids stumble on a dog and her puppies at the bookstore and try to find homes for them—while keeping it a secret from their parents.

name: Gizmo
summary: When Lizzie trains an energetic sheltie for a competition, it's unclear who wants to win more: her or the dog.

name: Snowball
summary: Charles meets a retirement home resident whose lifestyle makes her the perfect companion for a scrappy West Highland terrier.

name: Flash
summary: While visiting cousins Becky and Steph, Charles and Lizzie find a lost border collie. Returning the pup helps Steph appreciate her new home.

name: Ziggy
summary: Season finale. Charles and Lizzie rally their friends to help look for a missing dachshund. The kids may finally be ready for a dog of their own.

name: Guns Between Friends
summary: A firearms instructor seeks compensation for a valuable rifle he loaned to an ailing client; the defendant says he sold the weapon after the client passed away to satisfy a debt owed by the deceased.

name: Episode 7
summary: Woojin shifts her tactics after figuring out the real reason for the heist. Kim Sangman appeals to the thieves with a bold promise.

name: Episode 8
summary: The hostages set their escape plan into motion while Park Chulwoo calls for backup. Cho Youngmin's attempt to be the first to leave the mint backfires.

name: Episode 9
summary: The police interrogate a thief. Sangman steps in to take control of the hostage negotiation. A rescue mission takes place to bring a child to safety.

name: Episode 10
summary: The thieves offer the hostages a choice between money and freedom. After finding out about his son's love affair, Moscow reveals his past.

name: Episode 11
summary: A medical emergency puts the thieves on edge, while the deadline to carry out their plan is cut short. Woojin lures the Professor to a nearby hospital.

name: Episode 12
summary: The police close in on the thieves as they prepare to transport the money out of the Mint. Fierce protests force Sangman to put his foot down.

name: Accountants Have Feelings Too!
summary: Since the Accounting Operations Manager works with other departments on improving operational efficiency and implementing new rollouts, Sarah is busy trying to improve her relationship with the sales team... but that comes at a cost to the relationship she has with accounting team. Her new interactive role leaves Hunter feeling lost and alone, and as though nothing can really bring him back to his true self. While Dave pouts in confusion, Makayla tries to utilize the classic prank target of Jamie to bring Hunter back to life. Unfortunately, with Sarah and Marty, the Sales Operations Manager, hitting it off right in front of his eyes, Hunter goes completely dark... as in accounting goes emo.

name: 6 الحلقة
summary: Ahmad's father falls ill and is taken to the hospital. Elham's daughter terrorizes her for money. With a greedy intent, Marwan fixes Al Hajj up for marriage.

name: A Woman Unseen
summary: After running into an old friend, Miriam joins one last mission for the Inquisition to retrieve a mysterious object hidden at the summer palace.

name: The Will of the Maker
summary: A magister seeks to uncover the history of the Circulum Infinitus. The team distracts the palace guards so they can sneak into the temple vault.

name: The Serpents Coils
summary: To survive, Miriam and her team must get past the demons, hordes of undead and other magical forces lurking in the palace walls.

name: Those Who Falsely Dream
summary: An unexpected encounter with Rezaren and a shocking discovery thwart the escape plan. The city goes on lockdown as guards search for the thieves.

name: An Altar of Fire
summary: Looking for answers, the commander interrogates Hira. Miriam and her team return to the palace to face Rezaren and rescue their friend.

name: The Price of Salvation
summary: A betrayal reveals the true purpose of the mission. Determined to perform the ritual at any cost, Rezaren turns to a dark power for help.

name: Small Change
summary:
Life hasn't been easy for Leila Thomas. With an absent dad, a troubled mum, and nan no longer with her, it's her and her gramps against the world.

It's the run up to prom night for Leila and her friends in the Garw Valley. With money tight and the pressures of the cost of living weighing heavy on her shoulders, will it stop Leila's celebration? Despite the tough hand she has been dealt, and with only small change in her pocket, can a small change better her chances?

name: Bwl Boy
summary: Having recently moved to the village of Ynysybwl, 12-year-old Ricky Runner is tested by the territorial Bwl Boys gang. Ricky is pushed outside of his comfort zone into unfamiliar places by the gang's leader, Billy, and his courage is put to the test. Can Ricky prove himself a worthy gang member and find a place in the posse that has ruled for generations?

name: Heaven Is Overrated
summary: Bartholomew, an insecure, by-the-book perfectionist, is tasked with welcoming the recently deceased to heaven's waiting room. Peter, his first death, challenges him to face his fears, doubts and insecurities, with the hope that Bartholomew will send Peter back to the living. Will Bartholomew see the light? Or will Peter be forced to live the rest of eternity facing his regrets and unfulfilled potential?

name: Unveiled
summary:
Mim is a woman on the edge and is stuck as the maid of honour to her not-so-honourable 'best friend', Gemma.

On the day of the wedding, Mim cannot wait to be finished with Gemma. She has just been offered a dream job far away, but, with a problematic menstruation situation, their terminally hungover pal Bea, a manic photographer and the chain-smoking champion Auntie Anne threatening to capsize the day, it's up to Mim to make the day work so that the curse of Gemma's friendship can be broken.

name: Litter Pickers
summary: Debbie Harris is the leader of the red litter-picking tribe in Porthcawl. With just days looming before the big Clean Rubbish Around Porthcawl competition, Debbie gathers her troop together to go up against the dreaded blues - will she prove her worth to her fellow Porthcawlians?

name: A (Not So) Silent Night
summary: A young girl spends her first Christmas without her late mother. However, her grandad is determined to make it a Christmas to remember - but will it be?

name: We Love… Reindeer Bungee Fitness!
summary: Love! Love! Love! delivers everything you need to know and love this week. From music, pop culture, celebs and more - the team rundown everything that's trending! Max and Harvey take on the latest exercise trend - bungee fitness, and add a Christmas twist. Blue Peter's Joel Mawhinney shows us some magic, and adds some great tunes to our Add to Queue playlist. Shereen brings us the biggest hashtags and Video Hero, Piper, gifts us all we could want for Christmas when she reveals the Most Talked About Celeb of the week!

name: Amazing Houseplants
summary: Martha shows how to take care of popular houseplants.

name: Episode 10
summary: The easy relationship between Jin Xun An and Bai Lang kickstarts their coupled life together, but Bai Lang's sister feels worried about the developments.

name: Dionne Warwick
summary: Legendary Singer Dionne Warwick sits down with Chris Wallace to talk about her remarkable life, career and her new CNN documentary.

name: Tony Hawk
summary: Chris Wallace talks with Skateboarder Tony Hawk about the sport he made famous and why he has no plans to stop skating.

name: Dr. Anthony Fauci
summary: The Director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases, Dr. Anthony Fauci joins Chris Wallace to reflect on his long career, why he plans to retire and what he will do next.

name: Dessert
summary: Sarah Hyland hosts PLAY-DOH SQUISHED - the ultimate Play-Doh competition! Three teams of adults and kids go toe-to-toe in three DESSERT-themed challenges, all designed to test their artistry, speed, and skill. It all leads to the final test where they'll create their own Play-Doh world. One team will become our champs, and the others will see their creations squished!

name: What Do You Bring to the table?
summary: America's Test Kitchen is an institution for home cooks everywhere, testing recipes to perfection and sharing those tasty results with the world. For the first time ever, 11 passionate home cooks compete in the job interview of a lifetime. The winner has a chance to join the ATK cast, author a cookbook, and earn $100,000! Hosted by Jeannie Mai Jenkins, this competition is about to be lit!

name: The Test
summary: Mum searches for clues around the apartment building about a potential ghost. Vee's ex-boyfriend, A,  makes a return.

name: The Deal
summary: After his brother is arrested in a drug bust, a desperate Gurnaam Singh agrees to work with police. As elections approach, a deadly plot is hatched.

name: The Invasion
summary: Past tragedies continue to haunt Gurnaam. After infiltrating Madam Aulakh's inner circle, he goes after Mukhtiyaar Singh, a major drug supplier.

name: The Imposter
summary: Leading a double life, Gurnaam leaks information to police while staying close to Laadi. A police raid threatens to jeopardize his cover.

name: The Takeover
summary: A deadly fight ensues when Gurnaam's identity is compromised. Kimi's interest in singer Rocky grows while drawing Madam Aulakh's ire.

name: The Crossroad
summary: Madam Aulakh's horrifying past — and rise to power — is revealed. As the gang hunts for the source of a new drug, Gurnaam makes a shocking discovery.

name: The Escape
summary: As a despondent Sunny struggles to cope, Gurnaam anxiously attempts to get his brother out of the country and turns to Sehtab Singh for help.

name: The Deceit
summary: An unlikely family connection emerges, while a figure from Sehtab's past returns. Later, Madam Aulakh makes a proposal to Gurnaam.

name: The Masterplan
summary: Fueled by rage, Gurnaam seeks to avenge his parents' death. But as a deceptive truth surfaces, new dangers threaten to upend his life.

name: An Egg-cellent Adventure
summary: When Black Cat steals a sparkly egg from the zoo, Team Spidey must save it before it hatches.

name: Episode 9
summary: The stock price of New Data Technology plummets, and Hwa Young suffers a huge loss. She is soon accused of embezzling company funds. Miracle Investment offers to pay back the money she owes, only to acquire her shares of her department store. Do Jun asks Min Young to investigate Hwa Young's embezzlement case.

name: The Hangout Headache
summary: When Spidey offers to let Hulk hang out in WEB-Quarters, it quickly turns into a disaster.

name: Clarabelle's Pie Day
summary: Clarabelle is overwhelmed by the things she needs to do during Pie Day.

name: Sticky Science
summary: Duck, T-Rex or Gorilla? The Boys conduct a series of highly scientific (and hilarious) experiments to find the ultimate sticky tape, including the Shaft Length Pickup, Julian's Rip Test and the highly dangerous Kitchen Cupboard Strength Test. FOR FUCKIN' SCIENCE!

name: Minnie's New Puppy
summary: Minnie adopts a new puppy and isn't prepared to train her.

name: Carb v. EFI: The Multipoint Edition
Last to Know
summary: Micah finds a queer role model with a familiar face, while a new face comes to town and helps Dani and Sophie break out of their funk. Meanwhile, Alice tests the waters of her new relationship, until scary movie night becomes a little too scary. Shocking truths come to light when the masks come off.

name: Who's at the Door?
summary: Norman gives Nick a very special Christmas present - something that Christmas dreams are made of. But not all is as it seems - or is it?

name: Battle of the Babies / Norman
summary: Rocksy's rapport with Lindsay and Breht's now feral baby inspires her friends to get their own babies, and then make them fight. / Twig and Leaf reunite with their brother Norman and compete to win his affection.

name: Party Twig / Space Blasters
summary: Cicadas have hatched and due to a misunderstanding, they anoint Twig their Party God, leaving Rocksy, Berry, and Leaf in charge of keeping Twig alive. / The Mighty Ones have an adventure in "space".

name: Splintered / In the Pit
summary: Berry gets a splinter (Twig) and removing it turns out to not be so simple. / Twig falls into a compost bin, which turns out to be a fighting pit. He must face his cowardice and fight his way out.

name: Berry's Bunker / Matilda's Birthday
summary: An impending threat leads Rocksy, Leaf, and Twig to beg Berry to share her secret underground bunker. / The Mighty Ones throw competing surprise parties for Matilda's birthday.

name: Clover / The Moss
summary: A lucky clover offers to help Twig for a day, but once he's had a taste of good fortune, Twig has a hard time letting go. / Leaf gets obsessed with watching the lives of the microbes that live in Rocksy's moss.

name: Shellabyrinth / Helping Hans
summary: Berry runs away from responsibility only to learn a lesson of responsibility, and then totally disregard the lesson learned because being responsible is a trap. / The Mighty Ones meet a multi-tool named Hans and find uses for his various attachments.

name: Twig Is Dead / Message Slab
summary: Thinking Twig died under wet cement, the Mighty Ones make a statue of Twig and give him a funeral. / A phone falls into the yard while in autoplay mode. Twig and the others think the videos are instructions for living.

name: Sacred Cup / My Fair Berry
summary: Wanting a better way to drink water, the MOs go on a quest for something previously unknown to them, a cup. / When flowers invite Berry to The Bloomers Ball, Twig, who has a personal vendetta against the flowers, teaches her to be a proper flower, in the hopes of showing them up.

name: Pantsquest / Berry's Brain
summary: A simple brunch causes Leaf to embark on a dangerous search for cool pants. / Twig is the only one who knows that Berry's brain is being eaten by a parasitic worm that is making her act nicer than usual.

name: Chompers for Cobcorn / Boat Day
summary: Bernard steals Rabbit's teeth and when Berry gets mistaken as an accomplice, they go on the run together. / Berry's head grows to monstrous size and keeps growing.

name: Stand by Your Man
summary: Running away together turns out to be more difficult than George and Tammy imagined, with Tammy's past threatening to derail their hopes for marriage, and with George's past standing in the way of their future as a recording duo.

name: Mushroom Bisque
summary: Joanna makes a meal that celebrates her love of mushrooms (and bread).

name: Perfect Peach Pie
summary: Zoë puts a spin on one of her favorite pies after a trip to the bakery.

name: A Basement Kitchen
summary: Paul and Helen create a kitchen in the basement of a Georgian townhouse.

name: Mountain Cottage Overhaul
summary: A young couple takes big risks to turn a 1920s dump into rental income.

name: Canadian Landscape in Gouache
summary: Helen uses gouache to paint a colorful landscape of Canadian tide pools.

name: Little Weston Cabin
summary: A Connecticut couple renovates a beloved little cabin in Weston.

name: Charm City
summary: Preserving a historic Baltimore home reveals a unique Civil Rights story.

name: An Honest Day’s Work
summary: Eric helps a local farmer repair his 100-year-old cider press.

name: Call of the Siren
summary: When Axl uses her siren to part traffic for non-emergencies, she struggles to get the other cars on the road to trust her judgment.

name: Jamal's Jam
summary: Jayden joins his dad at work.

name: Julegaver
summary: In all its splendor, Christmas is also the holiday of consumption. Today's competition combines joy with Christmas presents and environmental considerations.

name: José Antonio, en Campaspero
summary: José Antonio is gay and has HIV, but he has never accepted himself because neither in his town nor at home has he found the support he needed. His family is by his side, but his sexual orientation and his disease are a taboo that no one dares to mention. In fact, with his father and his brother he hardly talks. Alone and insecure, he feels unable to face the comments and gossip of his neighbors. He is only happy when he does his show as a drag queen in Valladolid. He wants the queens to help him reunite with his family, regain his safety, and live freely in Campaspero. He will be accompanied on stage by his brother Rubén de él, something that José Antonio does not expect at all, and his cousin Alicia, a trans girl who lives in his own town with the freedom and acceptance that he himself craving.

name: World Tag League 2022 & Super Jr. Tag League 2022 Day 15
Episode 17
summary: Veering off from a world of glitz and glamour, 50 models try to slay a series of thrilling sing-along games in a bid to get their hands on the P1-million jackpot prize.

name: 10 December 1943
summary: There are plans afoot to hit the enemy from behind in Italy. Allied leaders are meeting again in Cairo to go over other plans, notably what to do about China and Burma. There is active fighting on two fronts in Italy too, though this week it doesn't go particularly well for the Allies. Attacks in the USSR are unsuccessful for the Soviets, but do well for the Germans, and there are Allied attacks by air in the Marshall Islands and over France.

name: 7 الحلقة
summary: Salma's mystery death becomes a threat to national security, which brings high-level officials to question Rawan. Rawan helps Elham regain a hidden fortune.

name: Happy Doh'lidays
summary: PLAY-DOH SQUISHED features three teams of fun-loving adults and kids going ‘doh-to-doh' in the ultimate Holiday Competition. The groups compete in two physical challenges that culminate in a sculpting event where they must build immersive Winter Wonderlands out of Play-Doh! In the end, only one team will win a grand prize, while the other teams' creations will get SQUISHED! Sarah Hyland hosts.

name: Sunny the Sun
summary: The chefs are getting ready for a wedding, and Jen is wearing her prized hat. Sunny Sun comes to visit, Small flies off to see how ketchup is made, and the two chefs cook a sweet and sour hat for their beaming guest.

name: Tess the Train Driver
summary: Jen is playing with her toy train set, but she really wants to go on a real steam train. Tess the train driver comes to visit, Small flies off to see how leeks grow, and they make a choo-choo party platter for their special guest.

name: Peng's puberty
summary: Temptation has come. Peng will be confused by his feelings. His blossoming has already begun.

name: Episode 1
summary: A search leads Uk into Jinyowon, where he runs into a mysterious woman who is planning an escape. Meanwhile, haunting visions of the dead trouble him.

name: Episode 10
summary: Chairman Jin initiates a plan to establish Soonyang Financial Holding Company to begin his succession process. He puts his trust in his second son, Dong Ki. Dong Ki tries to sabotage Do Joon by spreading a false rumor about Miracle Investment. However, Dong Ki only ends up disappointing Chairman Jin even more.

name: Bachelor Office
summary: Jenni helps a Milwaukee bachelor turn his spare room into a cozy office.

name: Urban Farming
summary: A young man's life is changed forever when he overcomes bullying with the Globetrotters' help; the Globetrotters learn valuable skills in food cultivation and healthy eating on the farm; Coach Lou puts a twist on a classic playground basketball game.

name: Clutch! A Demon Incarnate, Robin!
summary: After enduring Black Maria's physical and mental torture, Robin shows what she is truly capable of as a Demon Child.

name: Julebord
summary: The participants must prove that they have mastered one of the most important ingredients of the Christmas table. It'll be heels in the ceiling and teeth in the wallpaper!

name: World Tag League 2022 & Super Jr. Tag League 2022 Day 16
Выпуск 24. Ирина Мягкова и Дмитрий Позов
Spook Factory, 85
summary: New Year's Eve 1985. The whole group celebrates at Spook while facing their own conflicts: Toni to reunion with someone from his past, Lucas to his attraction for Enric, Marc to his fascination for his brother and integration into the group and Sento and Nuria to their inability to be friends after their comings and goings. And all of this, in the confessional of any self-respecting party: the bathrooms.

name: Heavenly Sword. Первая игра авторов Hellblade. [Разбор полётов]
How To Terraform Mars - WITH LASERS
42-Я НЕДЕЛЯ: «Редакция.News»
summary: "Who started it first", explosions at airfields, the verdict of Yashin, Strelkov returned, the exchange of Griner for Booth, a new monument to Stalin, "Rain" without a license.

name: The Kids Are Not Allright
summary: Sigrid's problems reach an absolute low point, and Pørni's attempt to help almost costs her a friend. Grethe is terminally ill, and Pørni begs Hanna to come home.

name: Gratulerer med dagen til meg
summary: Sigrid, Pørni and Princess Ingrid Alexandra have a birthday, but it looks like Pørni has to celebrate her birthday all alone...

name: Gediminas Žiemelis: turtai, grėsmės ir žaislai bei dramos karalienė Majauskas
Як ми (не) обрали професію мрії | ебаут + Андрій Баштовий
Token Joe
summary: Dwight returns to New York under unfortunate circumstances, where his reunion with his daughter and family doesn't go quite as expected. Back in Tulsa, Tyson runs into some trouble. Armand gets some news from Roxy.

name: Legacy
summary: The Black Mafia Family story comes to a dramatic close, as law enforcement makes their final play. Meech and Terry hope their legacy won't be written with them behind bars.

name: New Horizons
summary: Is it the end for one couple as two new singles arrive at the villa?

name: Is This the End of Social Media? With Ian Bogost
summary: Ian Bogost, author and professor at Washington University in St. Louis, talks with Jon about the demise of online social networks. In a recent Atlantic article, "The Age of Social Media Is Ending," Bogost examines the platforms' dipping trajectory and argues that people just aren't meant to talk to each other this much. He joins Offline to elaborate on how Twitter, Instagram and TikTok have sacrificed connection for content, friendship for sponsorship––and why a cultural shift in how we interact with these platforms may be closer than we think.

name: Episode 2
summary: Jin Ho Gyeong makes a family secret public. Jin Bu Yeon finds new shelter but realizes that her freedom is limited and time is running out.

name: Episode 11
summary: After Chairman Jin and Do Joon survive the car accident, Chairman Jin secretly looks for the culprit who tried to kill him. The three children of Chairman Jin, who do not know that their father is fine, begin a war of succession on their own.

name: Football Follies
summary: Peyton shows that in football, screwing up can make you a hero. Keegan-Michael Key and Jim Marshall join Peyton to reminisce on football's greatest follies.

name: Hold Tighter, Hug Stronger
summary: A family emergency forces Erin to rely on her team to prep for service.

name: Hot Springs Adventure
summary: Ian and his friends take another Four Wheeler adventure to Hot Springs Off-Road Park in Arkansas.

name: Veggie Lasagna and Berry Pie
summary: Learn to make quick and easy seasonal treats, veggie lasagna and berry pie.

name: Operaatio Melilla
summary: Andres (Fran Perea) follows the lead to Melilla to meet his old acquaintances. Hilkka (Riitta Havukainen) and Luisa (Maria Romero) weave a plot with the help of which they aim to find the main perpetrators of the criminal league. However, new discoveries cause more despair. Neither of them can imagine that Hilkka might also be in danger.

name: Episode 1
summary: Strike is approached by a woman asking for help to find her mother, Margot Bamborough, who went missing in 1974 when a psychopathic serial killer stalked the streets.

name: Episode 2
summary: The investigation takes a dangerous turn as a disturbing piece of evidence leads Robin and Strike into London's underworld. Robin risks her life by pursuing a vicious suspect.

name: Episode 3
summary: Spurred on by the father of a young woman who also went missing in the 1970s, the detectives attempt to outwit an incarcerated serial killer who may hold the key to the case.

name: Episode 4
summary: Strike realises that Margot's killer is responsible for many other murders that have gone undetected, and lays a trap.

name: Julestemning
summary: On Christmas Eve, everyone should be happy. The participants compete in creating the best Christmas atmosphere. With very varying luck.

name: Do Some Ninja Sh*T
summary: With the Final approaching, the players plot to remove anyone who stands in their way of the $200,000 prize and Challenge Champion title. At the Arena, the most brutal battle of the season takes place.

name: The Battle
summary: Kenpachi Zaraki removes his eye patch to fight Retsu Unohana, a.k.a. Yachiru Unohana, "The First Kenpachi." Meanwhile, Ichigo and Renji head to Hoohden to meet Oh-Etsu Nimaiya, the man who is said to have created the Zanpakuto.

name: The Blacktrees Prophecy
summary: Deep in Blacktrees Forest is a bombproof shelter built by a man named Warren Kaine. His extreme paranoia has drawn other survivalists to the village, and now a doomsday prepper group meets weekly. But after the controversial ousting of a member, Warren has a target on his back. Preaching survival at any cost comes back to haunt him as the Blacktrees Prophecy claims its first--but not last--victim.

name: My Next Guest with David Letterman and Volodymyr Zelenskyy
summary: David Letterman journeys to Kyiv, Ukraine, for a stirring, personal and in-depth conversation with President Volodymyr Zelenskyy.

name: Puss in Boots Can't Feel His Tail While Eating Spicy Wings
summary: Puss in Boots (Oscar® nominee Antonio Banderas) is the legendary feline outlaw and hero behind one of the most iconic animated film franchises in history. You can catch his latest adventures in DreamWorks Animation's Puss in Boots: The Last Wish, in theaters everywhere December 21. But how is he with spicy food? Find out as Puss in Boots takes on the wings of death and discusses his partnership with Kitty Softpaws, his love of leche, and his most memorable deaths.

name: Frozen vs. Fast vs. Fancy Food Taste Test
Jay Shetty Reveals His Highly Anticipated Rules of Love
Hidden Treasures
summary: Dolly notices unexplained things happening in her house: the shower being left on when she hasn't used it, money going missing and then reappearing, the radio tuned to the wrong station. Pearl fears her mother is showing early signs of Alzheimer's disease, but she hooks up security cameras to placate her. What they see on the footage leads to a surprising solution to the problem.

name: To Those We Love
summary: Pearl caters a wedding at a theme park, but the reception is marred by heated arguments and tensions among the guests - and that's before Pearl and Ruby discover the bride stabbed to death in the hall of mirrors. Mike suspects the groom, but Pearl has doubts. Worried for her welfare, Mike urges Pearl to stay out of it, but she can't resist investigating, even when it leads her straight into danger.

name: T-Shirt Throw Down
summary: A fundraising effort via t-shirt sales goes awry when a woman is dissatisfied with sample shirts and asks for a refund from a small business owner; a heated incident and a 5k defamation countersuit follow soon after.

name: Episode 9
summary: Richard's business goes global after a call from an international car collector in Singapore. And, Richard helps his best friend Les fulfil a childhood dream.

name: Vietnamese Cuisine
summary: Martha creates an incredible Vietnamese feast with her friend Monica Tran, including lettuce-wrapped golden fried spring rolls, traditional pho soup, and savory sizzling pancakes.

name: Sweet and Savory Apple Dishes
summary: Martha makes homemade apple cider, a tender pork roast with apples and braised red cabbage; and of course, we can't have an apple show without dessert.

name: Martha's Favorite Christmas Cookies
summary: Martha makes some of her favorite Christmas cookies with the help of her niece, Sophie; plus, Martha shares her incredible cookie-decorating techniques, and ideas for packaging cookies as gifts.

name: Gorgeous Gingerbread Houses From Start To Finish
summary: Martha's friend and food stylist Jason Schreiber stops by to help her explain all the steps to making top-notch gingerbread houses.

name: Celebrating Christmas
summary: Martha and her friend Kevin celebrate Christmas by whipping up her world-famous eggnog; plus, get tips to elevate your holiday décor, and ideas for beautifully wrapped, easy presents.

name: New Year's Eve Cocktails and Hors D'oeuvres
summary: Martha shares her New Year's cocktail party menu, and tips to make entertaining easy, delicious, and just a little bit decadent.

name: This Is My Night
summary: As Gamal tries to save his relationship with Sarah, the room plays every trick in the book to tear them apart. A new murder takes place at the hotel.

name: Buenos Aires Bank Job
summary: An Argentinian artist plans the perfect bank robbery with meticulous attention to detail and a bluff that fools the police. To pull off his subterranean subterfuge, he calls on his friend -- an inventor and engineer -- and seasoned underworld criminals.

name: Василь Кук - останній командувач Української Повстанської Армії
Bake, Bake, BOOM!
summary: Maya Rudolph and Amy Poehler welcome new teams of home bakers to the cabin, starting things off with a bang by asking the bakers to recreate a cake that just exploded.

name: Road Tripping in the 700-hp Hemi Gremmie!
summary: The Street Freak 1975 AMC known as the Hemi Gremmie has had some failures in its life, but now the 426ci Hemi-powered Gremlin is finally completing a road trip! In this episode of Roadkill, Freiburger and Finnegan drive from Detroit to St. Louis, MO with a stopover for a roll cage installation, and finally give the Hemi Gremmie the road trip it deserves.

name: Elves to the Rescue
summary: When Mum and Dad realise they've forgotten to buy the tree for their annual Robinson Christmas tree decorating party, helpful elves Biff, Chip and friends decide to oversee preparations while Mum and Dad pop out to get one. But not everything goes to plan, and soon Gran's mega mince pie has got burnt, and Floppy has managed to ruin the decorations. Then when Mum and Dad finally return with the world's worst tree, and the house is thrown into darkness thanks to a power cut, it seems like the party is well and truly ruined. Luckily for everybody, the elves have one last special Christmas surprise up their sleeves.

name: Episode 1
summary: The story of the investigation into the disappearance of a five-year-old and the challenges the police faced in trying to convict a local suspect. This first episode tells the story of the day when April went missing. People from all over the UK descended on Machynlleth to help search as police discovered that she may have been abducted, not by a stranger but by someone she knew.

name: Episode 2
summary: The arrest and criminal investigation into local man Mark Bridger, who blindsided the police with his explanation for his involvement in April's disappearance. As the media descended on Machynlleth to report the story, the specialist volunteers continued to search for the child further afield in the mountainous landscape, caves and surrounding mineshafts with no luck in finding her.

name: Episode 3
summary: A look at how the prosecution and police used forensic evidence to build a case against Mark Bridger for abduction, murder and attempting to pervert the course of justice without having found a body.

name: Jackbox Holiday Showdown! (Hosts vs Mads)
summary: MST3K is going to deck your halls and jingle your bells with a HOSTS VS MADS Holiday Jackbox Showdown where YOUR VOTES decide the winner.

name: Maya Rudolph & Amy Poehler's Celebrity Holiday Special
summary: Hosts Maya Rudolph and Amy Poehler invite their famous friends to "cele-bake" the holidays in a friendly competition to raise some dough for their favorite charities.

name: Homecoming
summary: Jesus delivers the most life-altering sermon in history. The result? More followers, more enemies, and disciples ready to follow Jesus anywhere. Simon and Eden reunite, Matthew faces his past, and Andrew visits John the Baptist in prison.

name: Luciadagen
summary: Baking enthusiast Ida Gran-Jansen is the judge when the participants bake Lussekatter. Blindly of course.

name: The Final Push
summary: The Challengers battle it out for their share of $200,000 and the title of Challenge Champion. Who will have the strength, stamina, and smarts to survive the grueling Final and take home the crown?

name: Kevin's Gavel In A Vice.
summary: Marjorie Taylor Greene says she would've organized a more successful coup, Kevin McCarthy still cant find 218 votes for speaker, and Sen. Kyrsten Sinema leaves the Democratic Party. Then, Sen. Brian Schatz stops by to talk about democracy, the debt ceiling, Twitter, and Hanukkah.

name: Кто и как меняет особо важных заключенных? / Редакция контекст
summary:
The practice of exchanging particularly important prisoners dates back many hundreds of years and has survived to the present. More recently, American basketball player Brittney Griner, who was convicted of drug smuggling in Russia, was changed to businessman Viktor Bout — in the West he is called a "gun baron"

How are such exchanges conceived and who approves them? How do the stories of the exchange participants end?

We discussed this with an unexpected expert — Francis Gary Powers, the son of one of the most famous prisoners exchanged by the Soviet Union during the Cold War. See in the new issue of "Editorial. Context".

name: Single Seater Hope
summary: Dennis Hauger, the Norwegian F1 hopeful, entered Formula 2 as the reigning F3 champion, but the season hasn't begun as he'd hoped. Dennis reflects on his journey to where he is now and hopes to end the year strong.

name: Freaks and Geeks' Samm Levine: Saved by Shatner
summary: Samm Levine (Freaks and Geeks, Minx) joins us this week and shares what it was like going from regurgitating stand up performances at bat mitzvahs to catching the eye of Judd Apatow and lucking into a role in the cult Freaks and Geeks. Samm talks about his time shooting the show and the panic that ensued as a young actor who just had his show canceled. We also talk about working alongside Quentin Tarantino in Inglourious Basterds, his entry into the industry via Lisa Kudrow, and how his impression of William Shatner landed him an iconic role.

name: First to Fight!
summary: The Polish state was the first to fall in this war, yet across the globe Polish soldiers are fighting on land, air, and sea as part of the United Nations alliance. The story of the tens of thousands of men and women fighting for Polish liberation is equal parts hope and hardship as they battle the enemy and even sometimes their own allies.

name: Episode 5
summary: A Baltimore neighborhood is transformed into an urban oasis where the bonds of family are in the farm's DNA; a company turns food scraps into black gold; apples.

name: When I'm Playing Basketball
summary: Mosley and Rob look for starters while the team prepares for a tough three-game stretch. Damani has a health scare.

name: The Heart of the Program
summary: DC's ego gets him booted from practice, Bryan struggles to overcome his Division 1 failure and Shemar's situation looks grim despite his talent.

name: Father, Consume Me
summary: Mosley tries to find the pulse of the team while a frustrated Shemar is a no-show, Bryan storms out of the workout and ELAC plays a nail-biter.

name: Game Hunters
summary: As the Huskies drop in the polls, Mosley shakes up the rotation. COVID-19 cancellations have the team searching for opponents — so they hit the road.

name: Mr Mosley Was a Good Man
summary: After some setbacks, the team gets an attitude adjustment from Mosley and begins to gel. DC speaks up about living in his father's shadow.

name: You Go, I Go
summary: The Huskies put on a clinic in front of some VIPs, but the games get more intense as the playoffs draw near. The pressure takes a toll on Josh.

name: Jump Stops Will Change Your Life
summary: A zip-lining exercise bonds the team before the regional playoffs where they're in a down-to-the-wire game. Dez opens up about being a good father.

name: Everything Goes Away
summary: The Huskies get the attention of Division 1 and 2 colleges with hopes of launching their careers — but first, they need to put away West LA.

name: Holiday Dog Attack
summary: A dog attack on Christmas day divides neighbors who fight over which of their dogs was the aggressor and who is responsible for vet bills.

name: What Every Sales Bro Loves
summary: In order to win the sales team over, Sarah tries to plan an outing to do their favorite thing: golf! However, when they find out it's only mini-golf, they can only justify staying by sprucing up the day with some fun "expenditures". Meanwhile Hunter tries to prove his value over Marty by beating him in a round of mini-golf, but Sarah seems preoccupied on the expense situation. When some massage therapists, hibachi chefs, and a live performance from the actual Holographic Tupac blow the day budget out of the water, Sarah has an ultimatum. As Lance says: you can't be a frugal baller! Accounting or sales, which is it gunna be?

name: Episode 1
summary: A new group of single men and women arrives at the Inferno, where they make their first impressions and find opportunities to connect while settling in.

name: Episode 2
summary: The women play a game where the winner gets to go on a brunch date with two men of her choice. The first round of matching takes a shocking turn.

name: The Cat in the Hat
summary: Host Tamera Mowry-Housley welcomes 9 teams of pastry chefs and cake artists to the City of Seuss. Just 3 teams will compete in this first qualifying round, using their masterful skills in cake and pastry to bring the story of the Dr. Seuss classic The Cat in the Hat to life, in the most delicious way possible. At stake: the key to the city, honorary citizenship, and $50,000.

name: Oh, The Places You'll Go!
summary: In this second qualifying round, host Tamera Mowry-Housley welcomes three more teams of pastry chefs and cake artists to the city of Seuss, challenging them to write the next chapter in Dr. Seuss's iconic coming-of-age story, Oh, The Places You'll Go! At stake: The key to the city, honorary citizenship in the City of Seuss, and $50,000.

name: Green Eggs and Ham
summary: In the third and final qualifying round, host Tamera Mowry-Housley welcomes three more teams of pastry chefs and cake artists to the city of Seuss, challenging them to write the next chapter in Dr. Seuss's world-famous story, Green Eggs and Ham. At stake: The key to the city, honorary citizenship in the City of Seuss, and $50,000.

name: How The Grinch Stole Christmas
summary: It's Grinchmas, and the City of Seuss has never been more festive! With the qualifying rounds complete, the top six remaining teams of pastry chefs and cake artists compete against each other for the first time, as they take on Dr. Seuss' iconic book, How the Grinch Stole Christmas. Only 5 teams will move on to compete for the key to the city, honorary citizenship, and $50,000.

name: The Shape of Me and Other Stuff & Yertle the Turtle
summary: Just five teams of cake artists and pastry chefs remain, and this time they'll take on not one but two Dr. Seuss classics; capturing the iconic silhouettes of The Shape of Me and Other Stuff, and creating a towering new throne for Yertle the Turtle. Only four teams will move on to compete for the key to the city, honorary citizenship in the City of Seuss, and $50,000.

name: The Lorax
summary: Only the final four teams of cake artists and pastry chefs remain in the city of Seuss. With the stakes higher than ever before, and the iconic Truffula trees back in bloom, teams will have to continue the unforgettable story of The Lorax. Only 4 teams will move on to compete for the key to the city, honorary citizenship in the City of Seuss, and $50,000.

name: Fox In Socks & If I Ran The Circus
summary: Just three teams remain in the City of Seuss to vie for their place in the finale! They'll be challenged to take on two of Dr. Seuss' most tongue-twisting tales: Fox in Socks and If I Ran the Circus. At the end of this challenge, just two teams will move on to the finale to compete for the key to the city, honorary citizenship in the City of Seuss, and $50,000.

name: Horton Hears A Who
summary: Only the final two teams remain in the City of Seuss to vie for the key to the city, honorary citizenship, and a grand prize of $50,000. To win, they'll have to compete in two rounds - first creating teeny-tiny desserts, and then with a design so large it's fit for an elephant, as they take on Dr. Seuss's grandest story of all, Horton Hears a Who.

name: What a Drag…
summary: Gudetama meets Shakipiyo, who has big dreams of meeting their mother — but the lazy egg could care less.

name: So Dizzy
summary: The duo find themselves in the middle of a bustling, chaotic kitchen. Gudetama accidentally gets separated from Shakipiyo.

name: Is That the Best This Country Has to Offer?
summary: Gudetama and Shakipiyo find themselves in the office of the Prime Minister, who receives inspiration from an unlikely aid.

name: Ahhhh
summary: As Gudetama falls from the sky, Shakipiyo comes to the rescue — will the determined chick make it in time?

name: You’re Rotten to the Core
summary: Gudetama and Shakipiyo continue searching for their mother, but to no avail. One bright sunny day, they bump into a rotten egg.

name: What a Cool Mascot
summary: In order to prevent Gudetama from rotting, Shakipiyo tries to mix with a dangerous crowd. But a hard-boiled stranger advises against it.

name: How Many Eggs are in that Omelet?
summary: Completely trapped with no way out, Gudetama, Shakipiyo and Hard-boiled make a deal with the Boss Omelet.

name: Give Up Already
summary: Separated once again, Gudetama gets taken to a local TV station where Director Inoue desperately tries to come up with a scoop.

name: We Wanna See Our Mom
summary: After Director Inoue drops them off at the restaurant, Gudetama has a change of heart, which deeply touches Shakipiyo.

name: I'm Pooped...
summary: Gudetama and Shakipiyo finally make it to the chicken coop but must now try to pick their mother out of the flock.

name: Foo!rtune
summary: It's been a few months since moving to Beika, and Hanzawa hasn't gotten any closer to murdering that certain man.

name: Amy Schumer
summary: Comedian Amy Schumer opens up about her past frightening habit of getting "black out drunk," her decades-long battle with reproductive health issues, her painful struggles with fertility, and a pregnancy that left her hospitalized several times before finally giving birth to her son. Schumer reveals her troubled family history of childhood traumas and mental health struggles.

name: Nick Cannon
summary: TV host, comedian, rapper, Nick Cannon reveals the story of his near-fatal Lupus diagnosis and the crushing loss of his infant son, Zen to a malignant brain tumor. In an intimate conversation with Dr. Agus, Nick opens up about how these heartbreaking, life changing events have become his greatest lessons.

name: Jane Fonda & Lily Tomlin
summary: Longtime friends and Hollywood icons, Jane Fonda and Lily Tomlin tell Dr. Agus their secrets to longevity and aging gracefully. From the foods that keep them young, to intimacy in their 80s and the benefits of cannabis on a good night's sleep, there is no topic that's off limits.

name: Anarchy in the U.K.
summary: Marc "Loop Daddy" Rebillet storms London with DJ and BBC host Carly Wilford. Champagne flows as they channel the rebellious energy that fuels this city as it re-emerges from years of lockdowns and political turmoil.

name: Amsterdammed
summary: Tinashe kicks off her European tour in Amsterdam, where she links up with local DJ and producer Cesqeaux. Together they explore the wild diversity and eclectic culture of his hometown, avoiding the stereotypical spots for a more real, raw experience.

name: Tokyo Calling
summary: Amidst her first international headline tour, Arlo Parks finds herself in the deep cultural waters of Tokyo. Guided by local DJ Sarasa, she's immersed in the blend of old and new that makes the city such a beautiful enigma.

name: Mi Gente
summary: Bas and the "Dreamville" crew stop for a long layover in Medellin, where prolific singer-songwriter Vince "Vibarco" Jimenez takes them on a deeply personal ride through the vibrant and colorful culture that has flourished in the post-narco era.

name: El Corrido de Monterrey
summary: EDM prodigy NGHTMRE meets up with long-time friend and fellow DJ, Americo Garcia, aka Boombox Cartel, in his hometown Monterrey. Together they set out on a taco-fueled 48 hours in one of Mexico's most underrated cities.

name: Born to Die in Berlin
summary: Rapper GoldLink heads to Berlin for his first show in two years. Local journalist and creative Cloudy Zakrocki shows him an unexpected side to the city as they explore its culture of transformation.

name: НИКОГДА НЕ ПЛАТИ ЗА ПЛАНИРОВКУ КВАРТИРЫ! #705
The Tree House
summary: Fanie struggles to trust her new partner and the pathology report brings more questions than answers, as another child is taken by the killer.

name: Wife #5 - The World Keeps Turning, No Matter What
summary: The scandalous news of a shipped actor dating a girl becomes famous, and many people are interested in it. Many fans feel disappointed in Achi, while most are still in a state of shock after knowing the truth. Fern is fired by Phee while the shooting continues. Phee tells Achi to hold a press conference to refuse any excuse. But what will Most and Achi choose to handle this situation?

name: The Legend of the Magic Pants - #729
Dana
summary: Dana comes to town expecting a warm welcome from family, but she's met with the opposite; some comfort arrives in the form of a new friend.

name: Sabina
summary: A nosy neighbour puts the wrong kind of spotlight on Dana before a nasty fall triggers a trip back to the past; Kevin gains first-hand experience of Dana's troubles as the pair are forced to play uncomfortable roles in order to stay out of harm's way.

name: Furniture
summary: Dana and Olivia search for the answer to what keeps bringing Dana back to the past; Kevin acts the gracious party goer at the behest of his hosts.

name: The Waiter from Two Nights Ago
summary: Back in Los Angeles, Dana and Kevin prepare to return to the past but have to deal with the familiar fallout of their travels.

name: Winnie
summary: Dana and Kevin find themselves back on the farm; a confrontation with Olivia makes Dana re-evaluate her purpose; Kevin must find a way to explain his mysterious return to the Weylin family.

name: Celeste
summary: The enslaved population faces unforeseen consequences from Dana's well-meaning actions; Margaret's search for Rufus's future wife finds Kevin drawn deeper into the family drama.

name: Jane
summary: Tom takes Kevin and Rufus on a trip to town; without Kevin's protection on the plantation, Dana struggles with a vengeful Margaret.

name: Alice
summary: Dana finds herself in a dire situation; Kevin chases a runaway slave; Tom seeks to restate order on his plantation.

name: Leeches
summary: While Nick takes the Big Apple by storm, Steve is back in LA staring down a discrimination lawsuit. Jealousy flares when Nick becomes a media darling--and the face of the brand.

name: Darcy The Mail Girl Interviews Charles Band
summary: This week, Charlie closes out 2022 with our pal Diana Prince, who joins Charlie to talk about horror movies and other macabre madness while also answering a bunch of bonkers fan questions. Get ready for a banger of a climax to a pretty awesome year one of Full Moon's Freakshow.

name: Our Little Peanut
summary: A teen girl with mysterious symptoms leads doctors to suspect she's a victim of medical child abuse.

name: We Do Not Forgive, We Do Not Forget
summary: A computer hacker targets Boston Children's Hospital to support the family's fight to #FreeJustina.

name: We Go to War
summary: The Pelletiers file a civil lawsuit against the hospital; Marty is charged with a federal crime.

name: And Then We Went Home
summary: The civil case verdict is revealed, and Justina navigates the path to health; Marty goes to prison.

name: A Norwegian Lifting Song
summary: Tara and Percy paint their new house and build a greenhouse in the garden.

name: No Estúdio com o Ex Caribe S02E09
The New Mr. Peanut (with Lou Wilson)
Main Event: Mandy Rose (c) vs. Roxanne Perez for the NXT Women's Championship
A Tribute to Santa Claus Conquers the Martians
summary:
Ride along with Joel and the bots as they watch a kidnapped Santa Claus teach humorless aliens about the true meaning of Christmas, in Santa Claus Conquers the Martians.

But first, we'll be premiering a brand new short riff, Bicycling Visual Skills.

Finally, stick around after the episode for a special holiday post-show event, The MST3K 2022 Yule Log: Memories Roasting on an Open Fire.

name: New Cabin in Tree, Two, One
summary: Shelly Wheeler grew up splashing around in the bright blue water of China Lake. Now, with a growing family of her own, and her relatives dotting the shores in their perfect summer cabins, Shelly and her husband Travis want to be able to host family functions at their own camp. The only problem: their camp is too small; so small, their daughter hits her head when she stands up in her room. With a growing list of issues and three growing kids, the Wheelers reach out to the Cabin Masters to help them renovate and resize their lakeside home. There's just one thing standing in their way: one of the largest trees in Maine - it needs to come down without breaking the camp or the budget.

name: Episode 5
summary: Rez shows musician Scott Owen a property near Belongil Beach. And, new agent Travis is in with a good chance to get a listing at one of the most famous celebrity hangouts.

name: Hjem til jul
summary: Before you can go home for Christmas, you have to pack, pack, pack your suitcase. And the participant who takes the longest must go home for Christmas themselves.

name: World Tag League 2022 & Super Jr. Tag League 2022 Final
Szabó Zsófi, Kabát Péter, Széphalmi Júlia, Papp Gergő, Sváby András, Frohner Ferenc, Sáfrány Emese, L.L. Junior
Will Smith and His Kids Take Over The Red Table
Puppets for Playas
summary: Lana reminds a rule-breaking couple about the pricey consequences. After an eye-opening workshop, one guy tries to get his former flame back in his bed.

name: Trust or Bust
summary: Two grenades bring trouble to paradise. Will more eyes wander just when Lana was starting to give green lights?

name: It's Raining Love Triangles
summary: A fruit-themed party sours with some shocking exits. Two people feel torn between their options — but only one of them is honest.

name: Jawahir, Jawa-there
summary: When Lana asks the couples to commit, will they stick together or fall apart? One person who's been playing games might finally have to face the music.

name: Growth is a Team Game
summary: A two-timing suitor is tested before the retreat residents look back on their time and vote for who they think deserves to go home a winner.

name: The Big Rig Job
summary: The team infiltrates a trucking company to stop a pair of siblings from stealing their father's company and forcing his employees into indentured servitude.

name: I'm a Ghost
summary: After meeting a stranger, Jess learns the father she never knew may have been a treasure hunter.

name: The Treasure Map
summary: Jess's life begins to unravel as she's plunged into her dad's dangerous world of treasure hunting.

name: Артём Дзюба - Про то самое ВИДЕО и ЗАВЕРШЕНИЕ КАРЬЕРЫ / Опять не Гальцев
Chapter IV: The Whispers of Nockmaar
summary: The journey leads the adventurers to seek refuge in the haunted castle of Nockmaar.

name: Episode 114
summary: For their third episode in South Korea, Arm and friends go shopping and enjoy a picnic.

name: Cross Country Rescue and Wedding Debt Denied
summary: In this episode, the Judge rules on two cases. Up first, a man drives 2,000 miles to come to the aid of his son and his son's teen fiancé, then is sued by the couple for alleged theft and unpaid wages. In the next case, a newlywed is sued by her sister-in-law for a trip and for wedding expenses.

name: Gran Final La Más Draga 5 Live
Chapter Six: A Christmas to Remember
summary: The Calvins race against the clock to save the North Pole and Christmas.

name: Oil Me Up
summary: The final five couples come to a gorgeous Italian olive grove, where they must transfer as much olive oil as they can to fill an a glass bottle using only their bodies.

name: Choosing Between Good and Evil (Mummy vs Daddy)
Best of Season 1
summary: Before we jump into Season 2, it's time we recap some of the best moments from Season 1 of Smallville… and there were a lot! Here's a little compilation episode of Tom Welling and Michael Rosenbaum revisiting the first season of the show that changed both their lives. This episode covers some of the major threads we got into this season - from FOTW, to risky stunts, to effects that were cutting edge, to suspension of disbelief. Hope you folks enjoy it..

name: Episode 11
summary: Jaebum regains his memories, but Sooheon is unfamiliar with this version of Jaebum.

name: Episode 12
summary: As truths emerge, the time for the final revenge has come.

name: Episode 3
summary: While In Seong is confused by the texts and call from the unknown number, Seon Ju believes it's a chance to track the caller. On the day of the meeting where Silver Lining's enemies within and out are gathered, In Seong collects all executives' phones using security as an excuse. As he calls the unknown number back, one of the phones rings.

name: Despite All
summary: All lies are revealed and the final decisions of the ten Pink Mates remain.

name: Episode 9
summary: Kanoon uprightly confessed to Namwa that she was actually a sasaeng and they both got into an argument. Meanwhile, MOM final was upcoming. Shokun suggested thag Gap should change his song for final round and find another woman singer to sing with him. Gap invited Namwa but got refused. Shokun wasn't surprised with her decision and he told Gap about Namwa's difficulties in the past. On the final day of MOM contest, everyone came to support Evening Sunday including Gap's parents. All of a sudden, Gap's dad collapsed on the ground. Paul and Gap took him to the hospital right away. Nice was so concerned about Paul, and promised to let everyone else know about their relationships, but something unexpected happened.

name: Natalia Lacunza, ganas de jubilarse y fotos que avergüenzan
Episode 9
summary: Ryota trains hard for the tournament, with Honoka advising him. Natsuko and Arisa are deeply moved to see the team united. Honoka's graduation is approaching, and the thought of parting ways with Ryota saddens her. Meanwhile, she hears that Natsuko and Aoki are planning the first-ever co-ed tournament. She meets with the director and expresses her desire for Kyoritsu to join but is told that they would have to win a league tournament in order to do so. On the day of the tournament, Yuma fails to show up. Without any other choice, Ryota and the remaining members compete and go up against Shikokukan University.

name: Noc miłości
summary: At a party for a hotel opening, Helena, Pola and Marysia face difficult choices to protect their businesses, family and personal safety.

name: Welcome to the Club
summary: After losing her business license, Pola decides to blackmail Władek. Helena continues to see Staszek while Marysia reunites with Jurek.

name: Chcę, żebyś patrzył
summary: Pola meets with Helena's contact at the Security Agency. Marysia teams up with Jurek to settle a score, but their relationship hits a snag.

name: Będzie słonecznie
summary: Helena, Tomas and Bogdan spend the day soaking up the sun on the beach. But they run into trouble when they stop for dinner at a local restaurant.

name: A seks?
summary: Despite Anna's wishes, Pola partners with Władek and Karmen to open a perfume business. Helena has second thoughts about her assignment for Adam.

name: O czym marzy dziewczyna
summary: After failing to find clients at the hotel, Marysia reconciles with Jurek. Jealous of his handsome rival, Adam takes in Staszek for questioning.

name: Noc striptizów wszelakich
summary: Tomas, his friends and Bogdan gather to watch the volleyball game. But the evening goes astray after they discover what Helena does for a living.

name: Nie wszystko od razu
summary: Anna and Józek's sudden disappearance shakes Pola. Marysia refuses to cooperate with the Security Service. Helena tries to sever ties with Adam.

name: Puchar Pokoju
summary: Marysia and Staszek run into each other at the university. Pola and Władek's family troubles get in the way of their perfume business.

name: Święto Piosenki
summary: Helena completes her final assignment. Pola finds new partners for her business while Marysia confronts Jurek and starts a new life.

name: All Exclusive med Sofie Linde
summary: Casper Christensen is looking forward to giving Sofie Linde good advice from a long life in the entertainment industry. But it doesn't work that way. The two get together in discussions about everything from gender identity to SoMe.

name: Bir Oyun Daha?
summary: Fuat wonders why the organization wants to kill the innocent Sefa Levendoğlu.

name: Get The Gun
summary: On the run, Cristo finds an unexpected ally. As new enemies emerge, Joe makes a big decision.

name: How Can Matter Be BOTH Liquid AND Gas?
Chapter 1: The Logo
summary: Two young black entrepreneurs create Eastside Golf to change how the game looks. But disrupting a sport as conservative as golf isn't going to be easy.

name: Chapter 2: The Break
summary: Eastside Golf is tasked with designing its first sneaker, and feels pressure to create something groundbreaking and authentic.

name: Chapter 3: The Launch
summary: Eastside Golf's first shoe release makes waves in the sneaker community, but Earl and Olajuwon are focused on creating something bigger and better.

name: Chapter 4: The Gospel
summary: Eastside Golf wants to fundamentally change the game of golf with its products, but traditional forces stand in the way of progress.

name: Chapter 5: The Reveal
summary: Earl meets with avowed sneakerhead DJ Khaled for advice on how to grow the business; the latest collaboration with Nike is ready for approval.

name: Chapter 6: The Grail
summary: As Eastside Golf celebrates its latest collaboration with Nike, the founders seek advice on how to build the business while staying true to their values.

name: Deadly Communion
summary: Vienna, 1908. A young seamstress is murdered in a luxury fashion house. Oscar and Max are initially perplexed by the means and the motive for her death, but further clues are revealed when Max receives a letter at his newly established practice. Together, the two friends uncover some dark and sinister secrets at the heart of the Viennese glamour industry.

name: The God of Shadows
summary: Max applies his neurological expertise to the case of a retired soldier, Captain Steiner, who is convinced that he is cursed and tortured by vengeful spirits. It looks like a tragic case of trauma-induced paranoia when the captain is found to have committed suicide in a gruesome manner. But Max and Oskar are not convinced.

name: Death Is Now a Welcome Guest
summary: When a famous film star dies during the premiere of her new film, both Max and Oskar are on the scene. Max admits she was a former emergency admission to his hospital, where he briefly treated her. Their investigation gets them embroiled in the dark underbelly of stardom and far-right Austrian politics.

name: Episode 7
summary: The ultimate psychological reality show continues. After a shock banishment set the castle into a spin, the traitors were given a chance to strengthen – but will their plan be successful? Breakfast sees one of the faithful keeping a huge secret from the group, and the players are pushed harder than ever to try to win gold for the prize pot. As paranoia builds, and accusations continue to fly around the group, a dramatic confession at the round table changes the game forever.

name: No Place For a Prince or Princess
Alaska Moose
summary: Steve and Clay Newcomb travel to the wilds of interior Alaska for moose.

name: A Tribute to Santa Claus
summary:
Come along with Mike and the bots as they watch Santa Claus pit his holiday forces against Satan in a battle for children's souls in Santa Claus.

But first, we'll be premiering Yet another brand new short riff, Bicycle Driver.

And after the episode, you're invited to a very special MST3K holiday singalong featuring our cast and the musical accompaniment of Paul & Storm!

name: #167 - Winter is Coming: Curtis Culwell Center in Garland, TX
Episode 1
summary: Dong Baek begins a new job but is surprised to learn that on his first day he has already been reassigned to the secretary department where he begins working closely with Min Yu Dam.

name: Episode 2
summary: Director Min reveals that he has been waiting for Dong Baek for 300 years and that the two must begin dating.

name: Episode 5
summary: One day, Seon Heo and Mu Yeong go outside to work together, but in an unexpected twist, Mu Yeong sees Seon Heo and an editor going to a hotel together.

name: The Reason Why It Has to Be You
summary: Seeing that Jung Woo is about to start a new life, Jung Hyun decides to reveal a long-kept secret.

name: Happy Ending Romance
summary: Jung Hyun and Tae Young try their best to figure out a way of getting Jung Woo back into the publishing industry, does their plan succeed by the end?

name: Julekort
summary: There are high demands for a perfect Christmas card, but it is now time for the participants to try it out today. Because the worst photographer has to go home!

name: Achcha Teacher
summary: Alakh Pandey, a genius student frustrated by the banal education system, decides to take a step towards his passion for teaching and joins a coaching centre where he comes face to face with his shortcomings.

name: Aman and Nagma
summary: With things stumbling professionally, Alakh finds solace when love comes knocking at his door. But will it last?

name: π
summary: Shaken by current events and unsure about his future, Alakh goes into the mountains seeking the purpose of his life when something other-worldly shakes him by the core.

name: E=mc²
summary: Rejuvenated by a new-found wisdom, Alakh starts his own YouTube channel, but soon realises it's not enough when Vyom Upadhyay comes back into his life.

name: Leader Log
summary: To keep its monopoly in the market, Youth Academy tries everything in its power to buy Alakh out. When it doesn't work, they try a deviant strategy.

name: Hero
summary: Youth Academy puts a nail in the coffin when they go all in with their plans to acquire Physics Wallah. Will Alakh succeed or back out?

name: В гостях: Шоу «Вызов»: ЕГОР ШИП, Катя Адушкина, Женя Ершов
Met Zulke Vrienden Heb Je Geen Vijanden Nodig
Oedipus Wrecks
summary: A surprising connection forces Deputy Director Bailey to ask the BAU to take a case involving young D.C. socialites who are bitten by a sadistic UnSub. But when the case turns political, the BAU finds themselves in the crosshairs from a high-powered senator. The team is led to a second shipping container that's rigged to blow.

name: The City of Flowing Light
summary: Bells Hells depart from their new allies and head to Yios, where they are quickly dazzled by the lake-top metropolis' glamor and gambling...

name: Black Hole Star – The Star That Shouldn't Exist
Giving With Your Heart!
summary: The holidays are such a wonderful time to give back and let the people in your life know just how much you love them. When you're giving with your heart, you can give a really thoughtful and meaningful gift that doesn't need to break the bank. The best present you can give is the one that brings joy.

name: Nostalgia Patrol
summary: Larry and Jane seek new purpose in Keeg and Kay's absence. Vic attempts to reconnect with his old crew. A mysterious invitation to a retrospective comes at the perfect time for a newly ousted Rita.

name: Paul Dano Needs a Burp Cloth While Eating Spicy Wing
summary: Paul Dano is an actor you know from acclaimed performances in films like The Batman, Little Miss Sunshine, Prisoners, There Will Be Blood, and many more. You can catch him in his role as Burt Fabelman in Steven Spielberg's new semi-autobiographical film, The Fabelmans, which is currently in theaters. But how is he with spicy wings? Find out as Dano takes on the wings of death and talks about working with Tom Cruise, the art of choosing roles, and his most memorable on-screen farts. Happy season finale, Spice Lords!

name: The Spooky House
summary: The team is called to the seaside town of Westward Ho! by Rob, who has recently acquired Seafield House, a 19th century former B&B. The reportedly haunted house was unoccupied for six years before Rob took it over. Rob is planning on renovating the property, but before he can reopen it as a guest house he needs the team to give it the supernatural all clear.

name: Trump's Grift-mas Miracle.
summary: Donald Trump gets into the NFT game. Democrats look to finish 2022 on a high note as Republicans squabble about Kevin McCarthy. New polls show Ron DeSantis beating Trump, as Florida's governor tries to out-crazy the state's craziest resident. And then New York Times tech reporter Mike Isaac joins to talk about the QAnon cult's new love affair with Twitter's new owner.

name: HUISBAAS MARCEL VAN HOOIJDONK WIL NIET DAT JE DIT ZIET MAAR HET MAG VAN DE RECHTER
The Laughter
summary: A vigiiante terrorizes Chicago's rental stores and is coming for Rent-T-Own.

name: South Suburbs
summary: While Turner experiences yet another disappointing birthday, Simon and K find themselves hobnobbing with the South Suburb's elite.

name: We Hug For 20 Minutes Straight... For Science
Как переживают холода в Европе, Украине и России / Редакция
summary:
The phrase "Winter is near", memorable since the days of "Game of Thrones", has become a real threat this year: winter and cold weather are now being talked about seriously — against the background of the shelling of Ukraine, Europe's refusal of Russian gas supplies and record electricity prices.

In general, winter 2022-2023 is not just a season. In our new issue, we decided to understand what to expect from it and how it feels in Europe, Ukraine and Russia.

name: One Flew Over the Cuck's Nest
summary: Julien struggles to show Grace's true colors to Obie. Audrey and Max suspect Aki is keeping a secret. Zoya learns of Nick's betrayal.

name: Eugene Levy wants to be alone
Mindwalk
summary: Desperate to warn Starfleet of their dilemma, a daring experiment goes awry as Dal inadvertently swaps minds with a Starfleet Vice Admiral.

name: TayNew Meal Date in Japan Part 1
summary: Tay and New visit Yokohama and explore the Gundam Factory and the Yokohama Air Cabin.

name: Sex & Basketball
summary: Whitney and Andrew attempt to bring their chemistry into the real world. Bela over-curates The Foxy's big spotlight. Kimberly accompanies Canaan to the Econ department's awards banquet. Leighton visits the women's center – and Alicia.

name: The Rooming Lottery
summary: When Leighton is elected Kappa's campus social chair, the roommates must figure out what sophomore year will look like.

name: Shattered
summary: A collision with the Paradox Prism sends Sonic to a parallel world called New Yoke City, where the dull environment looks oddly familiar.

name: The Yoke's on You
summary: A power outage gives two rebels a chance to break into a lab where the Chaos Council is studying Sonic's strange connection to their energy source.

name: Escape from New Yoke
summary: To secure the Prism Shard, the rebels battle the Chaos Council. Then Sonic makes a startling discovery about the events that shattered his world.

name: Unwelcome to the Jungle
summary: In a dimension called the Boscage Maze, Sonic runs into tree-dwelling versions of his friends who warn him of a monster that lives on the jungle floor.

name: Barking Up the Wrong Tree
summary: To find his way back to the right dimension, Sonic must battle the jungle monster who waged war on his friends and capture the powerful Prism Shard.

name: Situation: Grim
summary: Back in New Yoke, Sonic desperately tries to convince Nine to join the Resistance, but Nine is focused on building a brand-new home.

name: It Takes One to No Place
summary: In the tropical No Place, Sonic meets a friendly band of pirates and their mysterious captain, who loves to party.

name: There's No ARRGH in "Team"
summary: As Sonic's crew races to the Prism Shard, they quickly realize they're not the only ones after it. There's only one way to win — they gotta go fast!

name: Dollface
summary: The dolls are dolling! This week, the artists pair off into teams of their choosing to cohesively paint themselves into sickening dolls, toys, or action figures. Janet Jackson's makeup artist Preston Meneses guest judges.

name: La natura non si ferma
summary: Don Salvatore is out of control. Nino, with no more allies, devises a new plan while watching the rescue of a loggerhead turtle. They will take Teresa back to her family, and use the opportunity to get to Suro. To find her son Marianuccio, who has been kidnapped by her father, Teresa accepts. Their hopes, however, are crushed by the two families who have something else in mind for them.

name: Vitti 'a luce
summary: The power vacuum at Wowterworld allows Nino to adopt a new command strategy, one that is unheard of in the Mafia: democracy. Thinking about ways for the Tracinas to make money, Teresa has a brilliant idea: adapt extortion to the digital age. Christmas is coming. Will the clan manage to take advantage of the most magical moment of the year to extort as much money as possible?

name: /al·lor·quàn·do/
summary: The carnage carried out by the Mafia clans to find Suro's hiding place is spectacular. This makes it clear to Nino that to capture the boss he has to act more like a Mafioso than a magistrate. With the support of the Cosa Nostra families, Nino implements his final plan to capture Suro. What he does not know is that his sister and wife are also on the trail of the boss.

name: The Simpsons meet the Bocellis in "Feliz Navidad"
summary: Homer surprises Marge with the ultimate gift by getting her an unforgettable performance from Italian opera superstar Andrea Bocelli, his 25-year-old son Matteo, and his 10-year-old daughter Virginia.

name: Round 2: Drag Trippin'
summary: Happiness fills the halls of drag den as all eight queens continue their journey to rise to the top without fear of being eliminated. Since everyone is in a good mood, the drag lord wants to find out if the queens can manifest their joy into a riotous night of laughter and cheers. Will they manage to tickle the funny bones of Manila, Nicole and the guest "drag enforcer", comedian K Brosas?

name: To Lease or Not to Lease
summary: While away on vacation in Hawaii, a woman claims her roommate turned in a lease renewal without her permission; the roommate has another story.

name: Episode 1
summary: November, 2006. Detective Inspector Brent Hyatt and Detective Sergeant Jim Dawson, are summoned to University College Hospital in London to interview a man named Alexander Litvinenko, a former Russian spy who claims to have been poisoned. Litvinenko's wife, Marina, tells the detectives that the doctors are sceptical of his story, though the Russian's deteriorating physical condition is clear for everyone to see. Over three agonising days, Hyatt and Dawson interview the dying Litvinenko, who provides a meticulous account of who he believes to have killed him, and also the man responsible for ordering his murder, none other than Vladimir Putin.

name: Episode 2
summary: Watched by the world, the Metropolitan Police follow the radioactive trail of polonium across London, leading them to their main suspects, Lugovoy and Kovtun.

name: Episode 3
summary: A team of detectives led by Timmons's "best man," Brian Tarpey, arrives in Moscow to interview the prime suspects behind Litvinenko's murder.

name: Episode 4
summary: With their investigation complete, Timmons's team submit their file to the Crown Prosecution Service, which charges Lugovoy and Kovtun with Litvinenko's murder.

name: Litvinenko: The Mayfair Poisoning
summary: Explorative documentary following the investigation into Litvinenko's murder. Who were the people behind-the-scenes who dealt with a deadly radioactive poisoning on British soil?

name: Once Upon A Time On Draft Day
summary: In the Season 2 premiere, we connect our past and present as we travel back to Draft Day 2017. Here, Tasha Mack works to land a flashy contract for her new client, Garret and ink a deal that'll propel her to mogul status. Meanwhile, Malik tries to gain respect off the football field and college students Brittany and Raquel attempt to launch a vodka brand. And for Jamison, one fateful night changes his life forever.

name: Crash Landing
summary: Tasha tries to save her agency before the clock runs out on The Colonel's deadline. Meanwhile, The Fighting Fury stages their walkout but will the rest of the league follow suit? Brittany and Jamison deal with Allison's unexpected arrival while Garret helps Raquel navigate her burgeoning music career.

name: San Francisco 49ers at Seattle Seahawks
summary: Lumen Field, Seattle, WA.

name: Who Killed Santa? A Murderville Murder Mystery
summary: Detective Terry Seattle (Will Arnett) is back and this time, the case is critical. Along with his two celebrity guest stars, Jason Bateman and Maya Rudolph, he is on a mission to figure out... who killed Santa? But here's the catch: Jason Bateman and Maya Rudolph aren't being given the script. They have no idea what's about to happen to them.
