name: 17 December 1943
summary: This war has now lasted as long as the Great War did, but there's no signs of it slowing. The Soviets have three offensives going on on the Eastern Front, in Italy the Allies are attacking at San Pietro and over the Moro River, in the Pacific there are Allied landings on New Britain, but in Pacific Command, the big talk is all about a new super bomber.

name: 10 الحلقة
summary: Ahmad tries to protect Rawan from a social media defamation campaign launched against her. Layla breaks up with Marwan.

name: Paddie the Polar Bear
summary: It's the hottest day of the year but Small wants it to snow. Paddie the polar bear visits the cafe, Small flies off to see how chocolate buttons are made, and the two friends make chilly polar cones for their Arctic guest.

name: Doctor Dolly
summary: Small is feeling very sleepy today. Jen is having fun with her marble run, but she's missing a part. Doctor Dolly visits the cafe, Small flies off to see how broccoli grows, and the chefs whizz up a five-a-day pasta recipe for their kind guest.

name: Puss in Boots the Cat
summary: Jen has been playing in the rain puddles, but Small doesn't have any sensible shoes to wear. Puss in Boots, the magical cat, comes to visit. Small flies off on her spoon to find out how to catch fish, and the two chefs cook a fishcake crown for their purrrfect guest.

name: Gabby the Goalkeeper
summary: Jen is doing the washing up, but her hands are going wrinkly. Gabby the goalkeeper visits the cafe, Small flies off on her spoon to find out where milk comes from, and the two chefs make a power shake to give Gabby an energy boost for her next game of football.

name: Old Mother Hubbard and Her Dog
summary: Jen has hidden some toys in the cafe for Small to find, but she can't remember where she hid Dog. Old Mother Hubbard comes to visit, Small finds out how mushrooms grow, and the chefs cook up a tortilla pup perfect for their dog-loving guest.

name: Aladdin and His Carpet
summary: Everything is going missing in the cafe today. Aladdin comes to visit, Small whizzes off on her spoon to find out how raisins are made, and the chefs make a magical couscous carpet for their fairy-tale friend.

name: Goldilocks and the Three Bears
summary: Jen and Small are getting ready for a picnic, but the basket and cutlery are too big for Small. Goldilocks visits the café, Small finds out how porridge oats grow, and the chefs cook up delicious 'bear bites' for their bear-loving guest.

name: Jamie's Story
summary: Jamie has been blamed by his daughter for a controversial conservatorship lasting 13 years. Was he wrong to run her affairs for so long?

name: Britney's Story
summary: In exclusive recordings, Britney reveals how her life was strictly controlled. Is she right to blame her father, and was he wrong to confine her?

name: Andy And The Secret Pouch
summary: One by one, evidences are starting to appear right in front of Coby. Andy's secret will also be revealed.

name: Episode 3
summary: A debate surrounding a secret wedding ends with a shocking announcement. Jin Ho-gyeong tries to summon Bu-yeon back by causing her excruciating pain.

name: Episode 13
summary: Do Joon insists on using an aggressive marketing strategy on Soonyang Motors using the 2002 World Cup results he knows from his previous life. Upon hearing the success of Apollo, Soonyang Motors' new car, Chairman Jin Yang Chul decides to fix his will, which puts everyone in the family in an ordeal.

name: Entertaining Again
summary: Jenni makes over a kitchen for a couple who is eager to entertain again.

name: UFC Fight Night 216: Cannonier vs. Strickland
A Spell! Kid and Zoro Facing Threats!
summary: While Kid and Law take on Big Mom, Killer battles Hawkins and Sanji stuggles against both King and Queen, who try to go after Zoro while he is still incapacitated.

name: DDT Road to Never Mind 2022 in Fukuoka
Julemiddag
summary: The contestants must serve a family with very different Christmas dinner wishes - in true Countess and Butler spirit.

name: Takaisin Varjakkaan
summary: Lauri Räihä and Sanna Tervo return to Varjakka when the village's former police chief is found murdered in the forest. They get the help of chief inspector Jussi Ritola, who is weighed down by a betrayal from twenty years ago.

name: Elämä ja kuolema
summary: After the second body, Lauri and Sanna follow the investigation of a former police chief and meet Leena Niemitalo, who is in prison. A female theologian takes advantage of the Lestadians' confusion.

name: Chocolate, 83
summary: The group celebrate the farewell of Sento, who is leaving to military service. Nuria, who doesn't want to leave his side, turns to her parents to get them to use their contacts and give him an exemption. What she doesn't know is that Sento has his own hidden motives to go to the army... Marc, by himself, tries to integrate into the group and notices the fascination that his brother Lucas provokes in all of them, especially in Toni.

name: The Enchanted Sleeper
summary: Held captive in the hands of Mrs Coulter, a dreaming Lyra finds herself in a mysterious place with someone familiar - Roger. Will continues with his quest to find Lyra, meeting unexpected allies along the way. Asriel journeys through the worlds in his recruitment drive for his war against the Authority. In Geneva, ‘Father President' MacPhail meets a devoted young priest, Father Gomez, and sends him on a special mission.

name: The Break
summary: Asriel's plans change when unexpected angelic visitors crash into his republic, bringing vital information with them. Mrs Coulter risks everything to protect her daughter. Mary follows her I-Ching into a new world and meets two young sisters. Will tries to save Lyra from Mrs Coulter and the Magisterium, but it comes at a great personal cost.

name: The Intention Craft
summary: Lyra and Will are reunited in a new world, but they disagree on the journey ahead. Meanwhile, Mrs Coulter is put on trial in Asriel's republic and pleads her case for finding Lyra. And at the Magisterium, MacPhail prepares a new weapon to destroy ‘Eve'. Lyra and Will seek help from Iorek to fix the Subtle Knife, before reaching an agreement to go to the Land of the Dead together. Asriel decides to provoke Metatron, leading Mrs Coulter to make a decision.

name: Lyra and Her Death
summary: Lyra and Will journey through the Suburbs of the Dead and reach a seemingly infinite bureaucratic space. Mrs Coulter arrives at the Magisterium and tries to convince MacPhail of her allegiance in order to save Lyra. Mary begins to question her path, but she is buoyed by the unexpected appearance of a very unusual creature.

name: No Way Out
summary: In the world of the mulefa, Mary makes a heartbreaking discovery. Lyra and Will journey through the Land of the Dead in search of Roger, encountering ghosts who hide in the darkness, terrified of the creatures who fly above. At the Magisterium, an imprisoned Mrs Coulter tries to bring Dr Cooper on side. As Lyra and Will find Roger and vow to liberate the ghosts from their torment, Mrs Coulter puts her life on the line to thwart MacPhail. But can she stop him in time?

name: The Abyss
summary: As Metatron's abyss rips through the worlds, sucking Dust into its depths, Lyra and Will attempt to lead the ghosts out of the Land of the Dead.

name: The Clouded Mountain
summary: As the Clouded Mountain approaches, Mrs Coulter, Asriel and his council discuss their battle strategy. In the Land of the Dead, Lyra and Will deliberate their next move. After a rousing speech to the troops, the battle begins, and Asriel and Mrs Coulter face Metatron, risking everything to protect Lyra.

name: The Botanic Garden
summary: In the world of the mulefa, Lyra and Will reunite with Mary and hear a story that changes everything. But Father Gomez is also in this world, intent on killing ‘Eve'. Whilst searching for their daemons, Lyra comes close to danger but is saved by a forgotten ally. After an emotional reunion with their daemons, Lyra and Will are given a heartbreaking choice by Xaphania and Serafina. Lyra and Will must decide what they are willing to sacrifice if they are to save the worlds.

name: The Case of the Phantom Pooper
summary: 2IC Adam and Security Guard Calvin investigate a mysterious case after finding a poop on the floor.

name: Xmas Eve vs. Boxing Day
summary: It's that time of year again, where everything is magical... Until Christmas day is done, then comes the hell of boxing day.

name: Lisa-Marie
summary:
The award-winning transformational dating series returns to challenge single beauty queens to strip away their picture-perfect image in pursuit of love.

Former Miss Great Britain and now make-up artist to the stars Gemma Garrett was the original single beauty queen and credits the experience with helping her realise the road to true love starts with self-love. Now she's hoping she can help four brand new self-confessed beauty queens discover the same by taking part in a dramatic 'make-under' to expose their natural beauty before heading off on a series of dates with five specially selected – and completely unknown – suitors.

While the featured girl enjoys the dates, the three remaining girls, and Gemma, follow the action from the safety of the sofa providing supportive and humorous commentary throughout.

The series kicks off with 25-year-old Lisa-Marie, a skincare-specialist and entrepreneur from Rostrevor who loves to look glam. Full of fun, she's looking for someone to share her ambition and passion for life with, but will stripping off her make-up to meet five perfect strangers lead to total trauma… or true love?

name: Vivienne
summary: Episode two shines the spotlight on 28-year-old Vivienne, a human resources officer from Strabane. A hopeless romantic, this unlucky-in-love glamour queen has never let former boyfriends see her without make-up and admits the idea alone is totally traumatising. What happens when completely stripped of the make-up she relies on, she comes face to face with the boy next door from her childhood?

name: Joyce
summary: In this episode, Joyce, a 34-year-old hairdresser and salon owner from Belfast, in the spotlight. With a marriage and several failed relationships under her belt, she knows exactly what she wants from a partner – she just can't find him! She also knows her glamour queen image, and the larger-than-life personality it affords her, is intimidating to potential partners. Will stripping away the armour reveal a softer side and lead her to the man of her dreams?

name: Emma
summary: In the final episode, Emma, a 28-year-old marketing manager from East Belfast is in the hotseat. After a period of casual dating, she's ready to settle down and enjoy a more steady relationship but fears her glamourous lifestyle and image puts potential partners off. Will removing the make-up and dressing down help this strong, independent woman find the perfect partner?

name: Антон Долин о смерти отца, диабете и балабановской России
43-Я НЕДЕЛЯ: «Редакция.News»
summary: A swarm of drones, the delivery of Patriots, protection from Anglicisms, a leak on the Soyuz, a skirmish in Chechnya, Oxymiron against Morgen, the collection of bayans.

name: Matijošaičio problemos, pavogtas Jėzus, nuotolinis protestas ir (ne)gerieji rusai
Чому ми (не) зраджуємо | ебаут + Рома Геній
Stable
summary: Dwight visits Tina before returning to Tulsa. Pete agrees to send Goodie to Oklahoma, while Roxy tries to keep the FBI at bay. Dwight has an offer for Mitch.

name: Александр Шпагин о фильме «Москва слезам не верит» (1979)
summary: Александр Шпагин и Кристина Егорова разбирают фильм Владимира Меньшова «Москва слезам не верит» (1979). Фильм о судьбах трех юных провинциалок, приехавших в Москву учиться, а заодно искать счастья. Главная героиня полюбила, но была покинута. Однако она не отчаялась, сумела в одиночку вырастить дочь и к тому же сделать блестящую карьеру. Наконец жизнь дарит ей встречу с прекрасным человеком и настоящее счастье...
Jacob quashes a dispute between cattle ranchers and sheep herders. Cara informs Liz of the sacrifices of marrying into the Dutton family. Meanwhile, another Dutton finds himself far from home.

name: Astral Connections
summary: Shared secrets and an intimacy challenge threaten the bonds of two couples.

name: The Worst Tweets of 2022 with Rebecca Jennings
summary: Rebecca Jennings, senior correspondent at Vox, talks with Jon about the year's most chronically online conversations––those seemingly innocuous threads and videos that, for some reason, got people up in arms. Jennings' recent article "Every ‘chronically online' conversation is the same," describes the predictability of people being vilified on social media, and she joins Offline to discuss how much of our thirst for drama is really a thirst for punishment.

name: Episode 4
summary: Flashes of another's memory leads Bu-yeon to find out more about Uk's past heartbreak. News of a feared assassin's return shakes the whole kingdom.

name: Episode 14
summary: Do Joon fails to become the CEO of Soonyang Financial Holding Company because of Sung Jun's scheme. Just when he was despondent over the loss, Mr. Lee Hang Jae hands over the will Chairman Jin Yang Chul left for him separately.

name: Do You Believe in Miracles?
summary: Football's a game where fans truly can believe in miracles. Peyton meets up with the players who pulled off two of football's greatest: Herman Edwards and Ahmad Rashad.

name: Happy Anniversary
summary: Erin and Michael celebrate their fourth wedding anniversary at the beach.

name: Miso-Glazed Salmon & Snap Peas
summary: This simple, delicious meal of salmon and snap peas does double-duty.

name: Julegaveåpning
summary: The participants must show that they are able to hold the mask while opening Christmas presents they have NO way wanted.

name: Everything But The Rain
summary: Ichigo is kicked out of the Royal Palace after failing his test and finds himself in the Human World. There he is visited by his father, who tells him the story of Ichigo's mother, Masaki Kurosaki.

name: The Debt of Lies
summary: Challis Court seems to be a tight-knit community for retired police officers, but hierarchies from the force have remained--and resentments. When a new arrival is found dead, the other residents regard a murder on their doorstep as an affront and a challenge. Since Challis is a gated estate, Barnaby realizes that the killer is likely a resident… and therefore an ex-police officer.

name: Episode 1
summary: Trad Ar Fad embarks on a journey to one of the most exciting folk festivals, the Festival Interceltique de Lorient. Throughout ten days in early August, the festival showcases Celtic music and culture from a range of countries. It has been described as a melting pot like no other, and through the lens of Trad Ar Fad, we capture the atmosphere around the venues and other locations with Caoimhe Ní Chathail as our guide. This episode includes performances from Rura, The Bonny Men, Ross Ainslie and more.

name: Episode 2
summary: Caoimhe Ní Chathail introduces performances from the Festival Interceltique de Lorient, and we get a sense of the festival atmosphere as we stroll around the venues and locations. Featuring music from Ímar, The Karan Casey Band, Ards Comhaltas Branch, Dónal O'Connor and more.

name: Episode 3
summary: Caoimhe Ní Chathail introduces music performances from the Festival Interceltique de Lorient, and we get a sense of the festival atmosphere as we stroll around the venues and locations. Featuring Mec Lir, Perfect Friction, New Ross Pipe Band, Beinn Lee and more.

name: Episode 4
summary: Caoimhe Ní Chathail introduces music performances from the Festival Interceltique de Lorient, and we get a sense of the festival atmosphere as we stroll around the venues and locations. Featuring music from Brian Finnegan with Hunger of the Skin, Skolvan, L&R and more.

name: Our Best Food Creations This Year
Let's Play Challenge Special: First, Khaotung, and Neo
summary: Jennie hosts the cast of the upcoming series, Only Friends, and challenges them to a messy game!

name: LOL Xmas Special: chi ride è fuori
summary: LOL wants to wish you a happy holiday season with this Christmas special. A single episode hosted by Fedez with comedians from past seasons: Frank Matano, Mago Forest, Michela Giraud, Lillo, Maria Di Biase and, for the first time as a contestant, Mara Maionchi. With sketches, unexpected gifts, and loony jokes, it's hard to keep a straight face but… if you laugh, you lose, even on Christmas!

name: Episode 10
summary: Richard and the team try to win one of their biggest ever restorations - a rare 1950s Porsche 365. Plus, the team head to Silverstone in search of racing glory.

name: Episode 10
summary: After the music contest, Evening Sunday and Namwah take a trip to the beach.

name: What Do You Think, Gamal?
summary: Following their last loss, Gamal and the staff are fed up and decide to burn Room 207, unaware that their foe has been expecting them all along.

name: L.A. Hold-Up
summary: In 1997, a trusted employee uses his unique position to mastermind stealing nearly $19 million, the biggest cash robbery in U.S. history. He drills his loyal friends in every detail so they don't put a foot wrong while carrying out this Los Angeles heist.

name: Дмитро Грицай – начальник Головного Військового штабу УПА
Bake Your Fears
summary: Maya and Amy challenge the bakers to create edible representations of their worst fears; the Panel of Opinionated Grannies tastes snakes, spiders, eyeballs and more to choose the winning Phobia Bake.

name: Episode 1
summary: Kim Hye-joo clashes with her daughter after denying her a special opportunity. A shocking discovery throws the family into a painful situation.

name: Living a Normal Life
summary: Wook and his friends now try to live a normal life. Just as he helps a person from a scam for the last time, he becomes involved in a kidnap and murder case. Regardless, he looks the other way and plans to focus on his own life. However, a ghost appears before him. Ever since Duon, he has never seen a single ghost until now.

name: Recreating Christina Tosi's Milk Bar Compost Cookies From Taste
State of Emergency
summary: Bay City is on high alert in the aftermath of the brutal attacks. Pete races to the hospital with his newborn son and learns shocking news about his mom Sara.  Several members of the Garrett family have gone missing.

name: #1543 - Wells Fargo Arena in Des Moines, IA
Two by Two
summary: Jesus is a problem for the Romans. With pilgrims from everywhere setting up a tent city at the gates of Capernaum to see Jesus, tensions rise. Jesus officially sends the twelve apostles on an exciting but dangerous mission, causing Little James to ask why he hasn't been healed.

name: Familieselskap
summary: When the extended family from the country and the beach gathers, it can result in complete dialect confusion. Today, it is important to understand as much as possible.

name: Gebrochene Versprechen
summary: The department store Jonass has changed from a credit to a luxury department store - and Vicky is promoted to department manager. A lot has happened in her private life too: She is the mother of three-year-old Hanni and has a new partner at her side in Wilhelm, who is now even proposing to her. Harry and Helene are returning from the States where they have been for the past three years. Helene has accepted a position at the Charité and Harry has decided to get a record deal. But back home, Harry longs for Vicky. In recent years she has never answered his letters. Still, his feelings for her haven't changed...

name: Tracee Ellis Ross, Anuel AA, Aldis Hodge
Holiday Mailbag!
summary: Jon, Jon and Dan answer all of your burning questions about 2024, the Democratic party, the White Lotus, Taylor Swift, and more.

name: Почему Латвия, Литва и Эстония — самые жесткие противники Москвы? / Редакция контекст
summary:
There is a term "complex issues" in the lexicon of diplomacy. These are long-standing conflicts and painful problems in relations between countries and peoples. These are the "difficult issues" that make up Russia's relations with the Baltic states.

On the one hand, this is the history of their accession to the USSR during Stalin's time. On the other hand, the problem of the rights of the Russian-speaking minority. Recent events have only aggravated everything — Latvia, Lithuania and Estonia occupy the toughest position among the EU countries. The story of the "Rain"* is another confirmation. 

In general, it's time to figure out — why did this happen? And where will this neighborhood lead?

name: Hall & Oates John Oates: Wake Up Call
summary: John Oates (Hall & Oates) joins us this week to share his experience in the music industry and the ups and downs that come with being in a Rock & Roll Hall of Fame inducted, multi million record selling duo like Hall & Oates. John opens up on how he was able to pull himself out of the spiral his life was in during the late 80's as he wanted to change his image, was dealing with a divorce, and found out that he was being hoodwinked by Wall Street money managers. We also get into the mental health messaging that John includes in his music, who he was most excited to perform with, and some unfortunate things to happen on stage while he was performing.

name: Nazis: Neo-pagans?
summary: Books, films, and comics are filled with Nazi scientists and explorers travelling the globe to get their hands on ancient artifacts or summoning daemons with black magic. But how much of it is grounded in reality? Well, some of it. In the neo-pagan religion invented by Reichsführer-SS Heinrich Himmler, the world can only be explained through the occult.

name: TayNew Meal Date in Japan Part 2
summary: For their second episode in Yokohama, Japan, Tay and New share a meal at a delicious Japanese restaurant.

name: The Curse of the Clawback
summary: While everyone is dressing their part, there's still work that needs to get done. Lindsey is continuing to push the accounting team to the brink with her continuous discovery of control deficiencies, and finding of outlandish terms in the sales teams contracts, which could lead to the dreaded: clawback! Meanwhile Sarah and Hunter, not so subtlety, hash out their ongoing passive aggressive relationship battle as Marty continues to be his punny self. For Makayla, she has bigger fish to fry: her reputation. After a Tweet threating to expose and cancel her puts her on edge, she is on a mission to get ahead of the publicity before it's too late.

name: Episode 3
summary: Matched couples finally learn each others' age and profession. Back at the Inferno, disappointed singles take time to reflect on the events of the day.

name: Episode 4
summary: A charismatic newcomer captures Shin Seul-ki's attention. For the second couple selection, some follow their heart while others seek someone new.

name: Episode 12
summary: RJ finally returns to work at the bar. Bai Lang meets Jin Xun An's family.

name: Jungwoo
summary: Time passes by and Jungwoo returned to his daily routine. He is trying to live well by himself without Choco and Milk.

name: 1st Target
summary: Hanzawa has finally found the man, which can only mean one thing; it's murder time! But then, a certain master thief shows up.

name: Козаровичі. Підірвати дамбу, щоб врятувати Київ
ПОЧЕМУ НЕЛЬЗЯ ДЕЛАТЬ ПРОЕКТ ЭЛЕКТРИКИ ИЛИ ПЛАНИРОВКУ ОТДЕЛЬНО #706
Der Mutterbaum
summary: Kallie reveals the truth of what he saw, Sybrand and Tsedza investigate Simon's disappearance and Pattie's negligence leads to new tragedy.

name: Episode 2
summary: An unexpected visitor shows up at Hye-joo's home. Assemblyman Nam Joong-do attempts to divert the public's attention from his family.

name: Eun Hee's Killer
summary: The Industrial Complex Three welcomes Wook and Pan Seok. It turns out Hyun Ji had been living in the village until Pan Seok found her remains. Also, they find that Yang Eun Hee is a resident there. For Myung Ja's sake, they decide to find who killed Eun Hee and secure her body so that she may rest in peace.

name: Mr. T and Emmanuel Lewis in A Christmas Dream
February 31st
summary: As Steve's financial woes mount, Nick offers a lifeline in the form of a proposal that would take Chippendales global. A printing error has disastrous consequences for Steve.

name: The Messengers
summary: Marly visits Sara. Nardo returns to work at BCPD. Pete spends time with his newborn son Marlon. Evan has a close call after Avery tells him the truth. Lex stays close to Sara.

name: A Beautiful Mess
summary: Tara and Percy renovate the cluttered living room of their farmhouse.

name: Episode 10
summary: As the ultimate psychological reality show continues, and the number of players keeps on dwindling, another faithful does not make it to breakfast - but who has been murdered? During the mission, the players require laser focus to add more gold to the life-changing prize pot. And with paranoia and tensions reaching boiling point, the game is dramatically turned on its head, sending shock waves around the castle.

name: No Estúdio com o Ex Caribe S02E11
Main Event: The New Day (c) vs. Brooks Jensen & Josh Briggs for the NXT Tag Team Championship
Episode 6
summary: Braden reckons his listing at Lennox Head is perfect for an international millionaire to buy. Plus, Frank goes to auction with a bespoke bush property up in The Pocket.

name: DDT Danshoku Dino 20th Anniversary Book Publication Commemorative Tournament
Julefilm
summary: The remaining contestants will pay tribute to a legendary Christmas film, and a very competent panel of judges will assess the whole thing.

name: Papp Szabolcs, Kabát Péter, Megyeri Csilla, Hajdu Steve, Zámbó Krisztián, Dombóvári István, Szabó Zsófi, Pumped Gabó
Falcon
summary: Jack Ryan investigates a secret plan to restore the Soviet Empire through war, embarking on a dangerous op with the help of Rome Station Chief Elizabeth Wright and Head of Russia House James Greer. Meanwhile, an assassination on home soil forces Czech President Alena Kovac into a dangerous position with Russia.

name: Old Haunts
summary: Jack, out in the cold and on the run after the fallout from his failed operation in Greece, must evade authorities both foreign and domestic before receiving help from an old friend.

name: Running With Wolves
summary: Jack travels to Vienna to track down the source of his original intelligence on Sokol. Greer advises Alena on a key NATO deal. Petr Kovac, Alena's father, hosts a hunt in the Czech woods.

name: Our Death's Keeper
summary: In Budapest, Jack and Mike plan a sting on a slippery arms dealer to ascertain the whereabouts of the Sokol nuclear device, as Greer discovers some intriguing and potentially incriminating information on Petr Kovac.

name: Druz'ya I Vragi
summary: Jack and Mike head to a mysterious, abandoned outpost in Russia to seize the Sokol nuclear device, but an unexpected visitor foils their plans. Meanwhile, Petr seeks to rescue Alena, who has been kidnapped by her own head of security.

name: Ghosts
summary: Jack races to stop the detonation of the Sokol nuclear device, which has traveled to the Czech Republic. Petr and Luka's secret histories come to the surface in a deadly reckoning.

name: Moscow Rules
summary: In Moscow, Jack teams with Luka to expose the high-ranking cabal members within the government who are now orchestrating the secret Sokol plan.

name: Star on the Wall
summary: Jack, Greer, Wright, Alena and Luka all work in concert to prevent the start of a third world war.

name: Family Matters
summary: A murderer recounts the crime that ended one life and ruined his own. Those affected, including a police officer and the victim's family, also speak.

name: A Mother's Love
summary: In prison for killing her husband, a woman details her past abuse and her turbulent marriage. Her mother also reflects on their strained relationship.

name: Serving Time
summary: Years after leaving the military, Toby Gregory claims his service and PTSD caused him to murder his wife, Inez. But Inez's family believes otherwise.

name: A Father's Shadow
summary: Enraged over his rebellious daughter's choice in men, an extremist father enlists his son in a terrifying plot of intimidation and murder.

name: The Bogeyman
summary: Sentenced to life without parole for Jason Johnson's horrific murder, Gary Black says he has no regrets, while Jason's family finds purpose in tragedy.

name: Friendly Fire
summary: After fatally shooting a coworker, Thomas "TJ" Schifferns maintains his innocence. But details surrounding the crime suggest TJ had a motive.

name: Our Most Unhinged Moments This Year
I Have Two Lovers
summary: An impromptu coiffure change is Emily's only quick decision as she drags her heels over choosing a path forward for her career and her love life.

name: What's It All About...
summary: With Savoir spiraling into chaos, Emily reaches out to a former colleague for help. But an attempted détente during a glitzy gala quickly goes south.

name: Coo d'État
summary: Sylvie turns on the charm when working conditions deteriorate, Mindy gets up to risqué business backstage, and Emily makes up her mind about what's next.

name: Live from Paris, It's Emily Cooper
summary: While playing tourist in Paris, Emily scores a side hustle that puts her language lessons to the test. Camille hits it off with an intriguing artist.

name: Ooo La La Liste
summary: Emily tries to use her influence to land Sylvie a spot on a who's-who list, Mindy bumps into a well-connected old friend, and Alfie throws a party.

name: Ex-en-Provence
summary: A luxury car event takes Emily and her crew to a chateau in Provence, where lavender fields, a lavish meal and a surprise guest set off romantic sparks.

name: How to Lose a Designer in 10 Days
summary: As a double dose of fashion designer drama strikes Agence Grateau, Mindy asks Emily and Gabriel for backup after she receives an enigmatic invitation.

name: Fashion Victim
summary: Things look touch-and-go for Pierre as rumors swirl around his store opening. Sylvie reaches out to an old acquaintance. Emily supports a glum Gabriel.

name: Love Is in the Air
summary: Already feeling unsure about where she stands with Alfie, Emily finds herself on shaky ground with Mindy's boyfriend. Gabriel focuses on his future.

name: Charade
summary: In between undermining a colleague and helping Gabriel achieve his culinary dream, Emily attends a celebration in Champagne that takes a shocking turn.

name: The Turkish Prisoner Job
summary: The team uses the true story of a World War I P.O.W. escape to free an innocent man framed by a pair of dirty cops.

name: Graceland Gambit
summary: An old clue handed down by the Masons sends Jess and her friends on a caper to Graceland.

name: Chapter V: Wildwood
summary: Desperate to escape the Gales, Willow leads the group into the Wildwood, the unpredictable, enchanted forest, home to the infamous Bone Reavers.

name: And the Winning Couple is...
summary: The winning couple is announced, and Jerry and Rebecca give a live performance of the Love Boat theme on the main deck, complete with background dancers.

name: Improvising An Entire Campaign In D&D (Off the Rails)
Best of Guests
summary: Last stop before Season 2. This week we revisit our convos with some of the guests who were responsible for making Smallville the incredible show it still is.

name: Casino Bar

There's a lot to do and – on this occasion – only two days to do it!

name: Как в нашу жизнь возвращаются бомбоубежища / Редакция
summary:
During the Cold War, thousands of bomb shelters were built in the United States and the USSR: collective shelters were built in the Soviet Union, and in America, citizens equipped shelters in the basements of their homes. Hollywood even made a comedy about how a family, fleeing the end of the world during the Caribbean crisis, spent 35 years in a bunker.

This year, fears of a nuclear conflict for obvious reasons returned again, and with them the request for bunkers — and this time private shelters began to be built in Russia, as well as to revive the Soviet ones. In this issue, we figured out whether Russia will again become a country of bomb shelters and where to run in case of anything.

summary: All of Them Witches is a documentary exploring the history of witches, as a companion special to Anne Rice's Mayfair Witches. The one-hour documentary will explore an alternate and authentic history told from the perspective of today's most well-known, practicing witches, as well as scholars of history and anthropology. The film examines the provocative history of Witch Hunts, paganism and voodoo, and challenges the myths that have become the fabric of popular culture. Select experts featured in All of Them Witches include Pam Grossman, author of Waking the Witch: Reflections on Women, Magic, and Power, witch and entrepreneur Bri Luna, witch and author Amanda Yates Garcia and content creator and actor Curly Velasquez.

School's out for the festive season, so the mums (and Kevin) are busy prepping for the ultimate in blended Christmas celebrations. It's a full house at Julia's with an invasion of grandparents demanding endless cups of tea as they play with a VR headset Paul bought 'for the kids'. Julia has invited Kevin along too after learning his alternative was turkey crisps from the hotel vending machine with the other divorced dads.

Kevin excitedly offers to whip up a full-on Persian feast. Liz also turns up when her ex falls asleep on a train following a massive Christmas Eve bender, letting her down on his first ever offer to host. Meanwhile, Amanda is spending Christmas Day with Johnny, the kids and Johnny's new wife Tamara. Which is fine. Really fine. It's fine.

name: 24 December 1943

Generally, the Allied advance to Rome is turning into a stalemate though, but Winston Churchill still believes an amphibious landing is the way to break this. Joseph Stalin also has some pretty big plans to bring the USSR back to its pre-Barbarossa borders. In the Pacific, there is attrition over Rabaul and stalemate on Bougainville.

She gives them strict instructions not to 'open' their gifts until Christmas day, which leaves Julian struggling with temptation. The ghosts are touched by Alison's thoughtful generosity and are inspired to give her a special Christmas present to remember – but with Alison due back in a matter of hours, can they pull off their ambitious idea in time? Mike's loaded Tupperware comes in handy when their journey hits a bump in the road, forcing them to reassess their Christmas day plans. summary: A terrifying experience for Santi and Oly makes them rethink everything; while Vince and Reema's life will never be the same.

Meanwhile, a high school boy suddenly appears at Industrial Complex Three, asking to save his sister who is in danger.

name: Name A Number
summary: Becca, Izzy, and Erika bet how many. Of what? That's the question.

summary: Adam confronts Logan about the events in Bay City, Belinda makes an entrance and speaks with Adam. Steve arrives in Bay City, and Jack has a heart to heart with Evan.

name: How Star Wars: Obi-Wan Kenobi Should Have Ended
West Belfast

name: Billy Brasco
summary: Pastor Begbie vows to find an undercover cop called Donny who pretended to be his best friend and got him put away. He doesn't know that 'Donny' was Billy without his moustache.

name: Baby Love
summary:
Talk of a Troubles amnesty gets Pastor Begbie thinking about all the time he spent in prison. 

He remembers a guy called Donny, who he thought was his best friend. It turned out that Donny was really an undercover cop who befriended Begbie to get evidence against him. He turned Begbie in to the police and sent him to gaol. 

Begbie always vowed to catch up with the 'rat'. Thinking about it makes him angry again, and he becomes determined to track him down. What he doesn't know is that 'Donny' was actually Billy. After Begbie was arrested, Billy grew a moustache. When Begbie got out, he didn't recognise Billy, and the moustache has been his disguise ever since. As long as he keeps it, Billy is safe.

name: История самой горячей точки фронта / Редакция контекст
summary:
Last week, the military conflict in Ukraine turned 300 days old. In the reports of recent months, the name of the small town of Bakhmut appears more often than others. Vladimir Zelensky visited there, Yevgeny Prigozhin recorded video messages from there.

Bakhmut is located at the intersection of the most important roads of the DPR and the LPR — between Lugansk, Donetsk, Slavyansk and Kramatorsk.

What else do we know about this place and its history? For example, why is it called either Bakhmut or Artemovsk? We analyze in the new edition of the "Editorial Office. Context"

name: Paula McIntyre's Hamely Hogmanay
summary:
It's Hogmanay in the Hamely Kitchen. Chef Paula McIntyre is celebrating Auld Year's Nicht with a delicious festive supper.

On the menu is a warming bowl of cock-a-leekie soup. Paula doesn't do things by halves, so her version involves poaching a whole chicken, which leaves the meat beautifully tender. As Paula says, if you're harbouring any new year's resolutions, this broth, full of leeks and barley and parsley, will get you off to a great start.

Hogmanay wouldn't be Hogmanay without whisky, so Paula is off to Islay, where her ancestors are from, on a whisky pilgrimage. Joining her is whisky buff Lee Gibson. After a bumpy crossing from Portstewart to Port Ellen, they travel to Kilchoman Distillery in the west of the island. The journey proves to be worth it as they sample some whiskies made using traditional methods.

Back in the kitchen, Paula adds whisky to her next two dishes. For main course, she makes a malt and whisky lacquered duck with potato pancakes and a burnt apple sauce. For dessert, she shares her recipe for clootie dumpling, a traditional Scottish dish with a scoop of whisky-infused cream.

Along the way, Paula also reveals some of the Ulster-Scots traditions associated with Hogmanay. For example, there's first-footing, where the first visitor after midnight should always be a dark-haired man bearing gifts to ensure a warm and lucky year ahead.

Who is this mysterious guest? Will Ladybug and Cat Noir save Kagami? And will Marinette and Adrien ever have a chance to love each other freely?

summary: Lila is an accomplished liar. This evil talent has allowed her to be loved by all, and even to be hired by Gabriel Agreste. But Marinette and Adrien's growing closer pushes the boy's father to name Kagami as the new face of his brand, enraging Lila. She uses an incident in class to call for new elections in order to replace Marinette as class representative. But the campaign goes wrong, much to Monarch's delight. Thread lightly, for with Lila, things are more than often not what they seem…

name: 31 December 1943
summary: 1943 reaches its end with no end in sight for the war. In Italy, the Canadians take Ortona after bloody close fighting, the US Marines advance on New Britain, and a new Soviet offensive makes huge gains in the USSR. This isn't enough for the Allies, though, who have a big shake up in their European Command to help prepare for future attacks.

name: Нурлан Сабуров - КОГДА ЧБД? Про ТУР по АМЕРИКЕ, ПОСЛЕДНЕЕ ИНТЕРВЬЮ / Опять не Гальцев
2022 m. - svarbiausi įvykiai: karas Ukrainoje, Matijošaitis, Landsbergiai ir kt.
Episode 1
summary: Allison and Deacon are desperate for a baby, but they've run out of money to fund any more IVF treatment. So they decide to `borrow' the £50,000 they need from their rich boss Alfie, who they discover is illegally creaming off money from the company.

name: Episode 2
summary: Allison starts IVF and pressure mounts to turn the stolen bitcoin into usable money, so Deacon asks his creepy uncle to help launder it. Meanwhile, HMRC launches an investigation.

name: Episode 3
summary: Allison and Deacon do a job for Kethan but have another worry when a blackmailer makes demands.

name: Episode 4
summary: Deacon and Allison fall deeper into the underworld when they seize an opportunity to pay their blackmailer.

name: Episode 5
summary: Deacon and Allison make an enemy of Kethan and commit to a life on the run.

name: Episode 6
summary: Esme helps Deacon and Allison make their escape after Kethan and Alfie join forces to catch them.

name: Flora the Fairy
summary: The chefs are off to Granny Small's big birthday party, but Jen is worried as she hasn't got a present. Flora the flower fairy visits the cafe, Small flies off to see how jam is made, and the two cooks magic up some flower fairy tarts for their special fluttery guest.

name: Ruth Bader Ginsburg
summary: In one of her final interviews, the late Supreme Court Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg reflects on her tireless pursuit of equality for women — and for all.

name: Greta Thunberg
summary: Young Swedish activist Greta Thunberg's solitary protest for climate change became a reverberating call to action — and inspired a global movement.

name: Bryan Stevenson
summary: Human rights lawyer Bryan Stevenson fights for wrongly condemned prisoners and strives to change the narrative of racial equality in America.

name: Jacinda Ardern
summary: New Zealand Prime Minister Jacinda Ardern focuses on the power of love, kindness and empathy as she navigates national crises and barriers to leadership.

name: Siya Kolisi
summary: After growing up in poverty, Siya Kolisi led South Africa to win a Rugby World Cup as the team's first Black captain and began a philanthropic foundation.

name: Gloria Steinem
summary: As a writer and trailblazing feminist, Gloria Steinem sparked a movement among women while pushing for a future of equality, authenticity and respect.

name: Albie Sachs
summary: Freedom fighter Albie Sachs recounts his activism journey, the struggle to end apartheid in South Africa and how a car bomb nearly cut his life short.

name: Bizarre Love Triangles
summary: Little by little the secrets are revealed. The hidden feelings will explode.

name: Episode 7
summary: To save a fatally injured mage, Uk gives Jin Mu a firm warning and asks Jin Ho-gyeong for help, who agrees to cooperate under one condition.

name: The Smalley Family
summary: The Smalley family makes mealtime together a priority, no matter what.
